window.__LAKE_ASSISTANT_KB__ = {"version":1,"langs":{"en":{"docs":[{"id":"fact:countries","t":"Where we operate","s":"Lake Group operates across 8 countries in Africa  Tanzania (headquarters), Kenya, Zambia, DR Congo, Rwanda, Burundi, Ethiopia and Mozambique  plus a presence in the UAE (Dubai) through MERM and SAFF.","u":"africa-network.html","k":"countries where operate operations locations presence africa which country region","f":1},{"id":"fact:founding","t":"Our founding","s":"Lake Group was founded in 2006 in Dar es Salaam, Tanzania, by Ally Edha Awadh, with Lake Oil as its flagship company. It has grown into one of East and Central Africa’s fastest growing energy trading and transportation conglomerates.","u":"about.html","k":"founded founding when started history year established who founder","f":1},{"id":"fact:leadership","t":"Leadership","s":"Ally Edha Awadh is the founder, CEO and Chairman of Lake Group. He founded the group in 2006 at age 27 with a single fuel outlet in Dar es Salaam.","u":"leadership.html","k":"ceo chairman founder leadership who leads boss awadh ally management director","f":1},{"id":"fact:contact","t":"Contact us","s":"Our headquarters: Plot 49, Mikocheni Light Industrial Area, P.O. Box 5055, Dar es Salaam, Tanzania. Tel: (+255) 222 780 510 or (+255) 222 780 479. Email: admin@lakeoilgroup.com.","u":"contact.html","k":"contact phone email address headquarters office reach call telephone location hq","f":1},{"id":"fact:workforce","t":"Our people","s":"Lake Group employs more than 4,600 people of 21 nationalities across its operations.","u":"about.html","k":"employees staff workforce people how many jobs headcount team","f":1},{"id":"fact:fleet","t":"Our fleet","s":"Lake Trans, the group’s logistics arm founded in 2008, operates a fleet of more than 700 trucks  every truck GPS-tracked  hauling bulk liquids and cargo to Zambia, Rwanda, DR Congo, Burundi, Malawi, Kenya and Uganda, with workshops in Kibaha, Kigamboni, Morogoro, Nairobi and Ndola.","u":"fleet.html","k":"fleet trucks how many vehicles tankers transport haulage lake trans lorries","f":1},{"id":"fact:stations","t":"Fuel stations","s":"Lake Group runs fuel station networks across the region: 85 stations in Tanzania, 40 in Kenya, 25 in Zambia, 16 in Burundi, 10 in Rwanda and 8 in DR Congo. Use the Station Locator to find the nearest one.","u":"station-locator.html","k":"stations petrol gas station how many where locator filling nearest retail","f":1},{"id":"fact:lakeoil","t":"Lake Oil  fuel & petroleum","s":"Lake Oil, the group’s flagship company, is one of the top 5 petroleum distributors in Tanzania. Its Kigamboni depot in Dar es Salaam holds 38 million litres of storage with direct pipeline access to the oil import jetty, supported by 85 owned retail stations and a fleet of 300 tankers.","u":"fuel.html","k":"lake oil fuel petroleum diesel petrol depot storage kigamboni distributor bunkering","f":1},{"id":"fact:lakegas","t":"Lake Gas  LPG","s":"Lake Gas supplies retail and bulk LPG in Tanzania, Zambia, DR Congo, Kenya, Burundi and Rwanda, with 6 kg, 10 kg composite, 15 kg and 38 kg cylinders. It was the first to introduce composite LPG cylinders in Africa, and its Tanga terminal was built as East Africa’s largest LPG storage facility.","u":"lpg.html","k":"lpg gas cylinders lake gas cooking composite tanga bulk propane bottle","f":1},{"id":"fact:lakesteel","t":"Lake Steel","s":"Lake Steel is the first company in Tanzania to introduce high-strength corrosion-resistant (HS-CR) reinforcement steel bars. Its fully computerized rolling mill in Kibaha produces up to 25 tonnes per hour  around 100,000 MT per year.","u":"steel.html","k":"steel rebar hs-cr bars lake steel mill rolling reinforcement iron","f":1},{"id":"fact:concrete","t":"GCCP  concrete & aggregates","s":"GCCP (Gulf Concrete & Cement Products), established in 2010, is Dar es Salaam’s leading ready-mix concrete supplier, with fully-automatic batching plants, its own quarry at Lugoba, boom pumps and 20 truck mixers of 12 m³ each. Gulf Aggregates runs the crushing plants.","u":"concrete.html","k":"concrete gccp ready-mix cement aggregate quarry batching premix gulf","f":1},{"id":"fact:lubricants","t":"Lake Lubes  lubricants","s":"Lake Lubes, incorporated in Dar es Salaam in 2014, manufactures and distributes lubricants and greases  including LAKE 4T, LAKE HD SUPREME, LAKE POWER, gear oils, ATF, coolants and greases  sold through the Lake Oil station network and across the group’s countries, with 24/7 technical after-sales support.","u":"lubricants.html","k":"lubricants oil grease lake lubes engine motor coolant gear","f":1},{"id":"fact:containers","t":"Container services","s":"AFICD (African Inland Container Depot) provides ICD, CFS and empty-container services at Tazara, Pugu Road, Dar es Salaam  a 14,000 m² yard with 4,000 TEU capacity and a rail siding to the port  serving Rwanda, Burundi, Uganda, DR Congo, Zambia and Malawi. ACFS adds a 5,000 TEU cargo freight station.","u":"container-services.html","k":"container icd cfs aficd acfs depot teu shipping freight port","f":1},{"id":"fact:subsidiaries","t":"Group companies","s":"Lake Group’s main companies are Lake Oil (fuel & petroleum), Lake Gas (LPG), Lake Trans (logistics), Lake Lubes (lubricants), Lake Steel (HS-CR rebar), GCCP and Gulf Aggregates (concrete & aggregates), AFICD and ACFS (container services), plus MERM (ready-mix) and SAFF (freight forwarding) in Dubai.","u":"services.html","k":"subsidiaries companies divisions group businesses sectors what do you do services brands","f":1},{"id":"fact:careers","t":"Careers","s":"We are always looking for talented people across our group companies in 8 countries. Visit the Careers page to explore current opportunities and apply.","u":"careers.html","k":"careers jobs vacancies hiring work employment apply recruitment opportunity","f":1},{"id":"fact:values","t":"Values & culture","s":"Lake Group’s core values are Teamwork, Reliability, Integrity and Customer Satisfaction, backed by a culture of Quality, Service, Safety and Professionalism.","u":"about.html","k":"values culture mission vision principles quality safety","f":1},{"id":"pg:hero:0","t":"Home","s":"Est. 2006 · Dar es Salaam, Tanzania Powering East & Central Africa One of Africa's fastest-growing energy, logistics & construction conglomerates, operating across 8 countries with 4,600+ employees and 700+ trucks on the road.","u":"index.html"},{"id":"pg:ose:0","t":"About","s":"At 27 years old, Ally Edha Awadh opened a single fuel outlet in Dar es Salaam. No fleet, no network, no certainty. Just a belief that East Africa deserved a more reliable energy supply chain. Ally Edha Awadh, Founder & Chairman Lake Trans: bulk haulage across East Africa Lake Gas now supplies LPG cylinders to six countries, displacing charcoal stoves and giving families a safer way to cook.","u":"our-story.html"},{"id":"pg:ose:1","t":"About","s":"We built more than a fuel company. GCCP: Dar es Salaam's leading ready-mix concrete supplier Every depot, every truck, every cylinder is run by people. 4,600+ of them, from 21 nationalities, across 8 countries. That's the part no spreadsheet can capture. across 8 countries and counting. Tanzania &middot; Kenya &middot; Zambia &middot; Rwanda &middot; Burundi &middot; DRC &middot; Ethiopia &middot; Mozambique","u":"our-story.html"},{"id":"pg:ose:2","t":"About","s":"Quality. Service. Safety. Professionalism. Powering East & Central Africa since 2006. \"From a single fuel outlet to one of East Africa's largest energy and industrial conglomerates.\"","u":"our-story.html"},{"id":"pg:about:0","t":"About","s":"One of East and Central Africa's fastest growing energy trading and transportation conglomerates, founded 2006. From a Single Fuel Company to a Regional Powerhouse Lake Group was established by its founding CEO and Chairman Mr. Ally Edha Awadh in 2006 with the opening of its flagship company, Lake Oil: a humble beginning in Dar es Salaam, Tanzania.","u":"about.html"},{"id":"pg:about:1","t":"About","s":"Since inception, the growth story of Lake Group has been vertical, becoming one of the fastest-growing energy trading, logistics and construction supply material conglomerates in East and Central Africa and the Middle East. Today, Lake Group distributes petroleum products in 8 countries, owns storage facilities across the region, manufactures lubricants and ready-mix concrete, and operates a fleet of more than 700 trucks.","u":"about.html"},{"id":"pg:about:2","t":"About","s":"With a diverse mix of 21 nationalities and a total workforce of 4,600+ employees, Lake Group continues to grow with purpose. To provide customers with quality products and services in a safe, efficient and cost-effective manner without damaging the environment, identifying and entering new areas of business while creating a work environment where employees exceed their personal best.","u":"about.html"},{"id":"pg:about:3","t":"About","s":"Guided by our core values: Teamwork, Reliability, Integrity and Customer Satisfaction. Teamwork, Reliability, Integrity To become the leading regional convenience retailer and marketer of products and services while achieving continuous improvement through operational excellence, innovation and a culture based on performance. Founded Lake Group at age 27 in 2006","u":"about.html"},{"id":"pg:about:4","t":"About","s":"\"Welcome to a diverse pioneer in fuel marketing, haulage, LPG bottling, cylinder manufacturing and concrete production. With our experienced team across all business units, we are fully geared to meet the demands of the global marketplace.\" Under Mr. Awadh's leadership, Lake Group has successfully established itself in Oil & Gas, Engineering, Industrial Supplies, Projects, Cargo, Distribution, General Trading, Storage, Concrete Solutions and the Construction Sector, building a high-credit-rated organisation over nearly two decades.","u":"about.html"},{"id":"pg:about:5","t":"About","s":"© 2026 Lake Group. All rights reserved.","u":"about.html"},{"id":"pg:africa_network:0","t":"Africa Operations Map","s":"Interactive map of Lake Group's presence across 8 countries in East and Central Africa, plus Dubai. 85+ Fuel Stations, Blue, White, Yellow & Red 700+ Trucks · 4,600+ Employees Spread Across Every Corner of East & Central Africa Lake Group is geographically spread across every region of Tanzania and neighbouring countries of Zambia, DRC, Burundi, Rwanda and Kenya, with operations in Ethiopia, Mozambique and a major premix plant in Dubai.","u":"africa-network.html"},{"id":"pg:africa_network:1","t":"Africa Operations Map","s":"Our petrol stations are instantly recognisable in eye-catching blue, white, yellow and red, the same bold Lake Group colours you'll see on the map below. eye-catching blue, white, yellow and red Headquarters · 10 subsidiaries Lake Oil Ltd.: Petroleum Distribution Lake Trans Ltd.: Transport & Haulage Lake Gas Ltd.: LPG Bottling & Distribution Lake Lubes Ltd.: Lubricants Manufacturing","u":"africa-network.html"},{"id":"pg:africa_network:2","t":"Africa Operations Map","s":"Lake Steel Ltd.: HS-CR Steel Rolling Mill GCCP Co. Ltd.: Ready-Mix Concrete AFICD: African Inland Container Depot ACFS: Container Freight Station SAFF: Freight Forwarding & Shipping Gulf Aggregate: Stone Crushing Lake Gas Ltd.: LPG Distribution MERM: Middle East Ready Mix LLC One of Lake Group's largest premix concrete operations, serving major construction projects in Dubai.","u":"africa-network.html"},{"id":"pg:africa_network:3","t":"Africa Operations Map","s":"Country borders shown in white · Lake Group nations in gold · Colored dots = infrastructure Why Lake Group Stands Out Across Africa The same principles that power our homepage, quality, service, safety and professionalism, guide every market we operate in. No compromise on quality, from fuel and LPG to steel, lubricants and ready-mix concrete.","u":"africa-network.html"},{"id":"pg:africa_network:4","t":"Africa Operations Map","s":"Highest service standards and consistent supply of fuel and customer care in every territory. Safety is first in all we do, across depots, haulage fleets, LPG terminals and construction sites. Professionalism is the culture we cherish, 4,600+ staff from 21 nationalities, one team. Operations Across the Continent Fuel depots, LPG terminals, truck fleets, container depots and concrete plants, all connected through our Africa network.","u":"africa-network.html"},{"id":"pg:africa_network:5","t":"Africa Operations Map","s":"© 2026 Lake Group. All rights reserved.","u":"africa-network.html"},{"id":"pg:careers:0","t":"Careers","s":"We are always looking for talented, driven professionals to join our growing team across East and Central Africa. Build Your Career Across Africa Lake Group offers careers with real impact, you'll work across one of East Africa's most dynamic businesses, with genuine opportunities to grow, lead and make a difference. With 4,600+ employees across 8 countries and 21 nationalities, we are a truly pan-African team united by shared values: Quality, Service, Safety and Professionalism.","u":"careers.html"},{"id":"pg:careers:1","t":"Careers","s":"Cross-country and cross-division advancement opportunities Work on projects that shape East Africa's development Work alongside 21 nationalities across 8 countries Industry-leading safety standards in all operations Depots, terminals & plants across the Group Even if no specific role matches your profile, we welcome speculative applications from talented professionals.","u":"careers.html"},{"id":"pg:careers:2","t":"Careers","s":"© 2026 Lake Group. All rights reserved. Tell us about yourself and what you bring to Lake Group...","u":"careers.html"},{"id":"pg:concrete:0","t":"Concrete & Aggregate","s":"Ready-Mix Concrete & Aggregate Gulf Concrete and Cement Products, Dar es Salaam's market-leading ready-mix concrete supplier since 2010. Gulf Concrete and Cement Products Company Ltd (GCCP), established in 2010, is one of the leading suppliers of ready-mix concrete in Dar es Salaam, involved in many of the city's most prestigious construction projects.","u":"concrete.html"},{"id":"pg:concrete:1","t":"Concrete & Aggregate","s":"GCCP operates its own quarry at Lugoba with two aggregate plants of 250 tons/hour capacity each, producing 30,000 m³ of aggregate monthly. Its ready-mix operations are powered by Sany International batching plants from China. In Dubai, Lake Group operates MERM (Middle East Ready Mix LLC), one of the largest premix plants in the region. MERM (Middle East Ready Mix LLC)","u":"concrete.html"},{"id":"pg:concrete:2","t":"Concrete & Aggregate","s":"✓Fully-automatic Sany International batching plants ✓2x Aggregate crushing plants (250T/hr each) ✓4 stationary concrete pumps (Sany International) ✓2 boom pumps (32m boom length) ✓Own quarry at Lugoba, Tanzania Ultra-Rapid Hardening Concrete For projects requiring fast formwork removal and accelerated construction schedules. Low shrinkage formulation for slabs, pavements and structures where crack control is critical.","u":"concrete.html"},{"id":"pg:concrete:3","t":"Concrete & Aggregate","s":"Self-Consolidating Concrete (SCC) Flows and consolidates under its own weight, ideal for congested reinforcement. High-finish concrete for facades, decorative surfaces and exposed structural elements. Permeable concrete for sustainable drainage in car parks, roads and landscaping. High-strength, highly durable concrete for piling, deep foundations and critical structures.","u":"concrete.html"},{"id":"pg:concrete:4","t":"Concrete & Aggregate","s":"© 2026 Lake Group. All rights reserved.","u":"concrete.html"},{"id":"pg:contact:0","t":"Contact","s":"Reach our team for enquiries, partnerships, quotes or any information about Lake Group and its subsidiaries. Plot 49, Mikocheni Light Industrial Area P.O.BOX 5055, Dar es Salaam, Tanzania Mikocheni, Dar es Salaam, Tanzania Coordinates: -6.762806, 39.241447 © 2026 Lake Group. All rights reserved.","u":"contact.html"},{"id":"pg:container_services:0","t":"Container Services","s":"African Inland Container Depot (AFICD) and Container Freight Station (ACFS), port extension solutions across East Africa. The Inland Gateway to East African Trade AFICD (African Inland Container Depot) and ACFS (African Container Freight Station) are Lake Group's port logistics arms, providing critical container storage, handling and customs services that extend port capacity into the hinterland.","u":"container-services.html"},{"id":"pg:container_services:1","t":"Container Services","s":"With operations in Tanzania, Zambia and Mozambique, our container services are positioned at strategic corridors to serve regional importers, exporters and shipping lines. ✓Container storage and stacking ✓Container stuffing and de-stuffing (LCL/FCL) ✓Customs examination and clearance support ✓Reefer (refrigerated) container handling ✓Container repair and maintenance","u":"container-services.html"},{"id":"pg:container_services:2","t":"Container Services","s":"✓Integration with Lake Trans trucking network Dar es Salaam, gateway to East Africa's largest economy Inland depot serving the Zambia-Tanzania corridor Strategic port logistics for Beira corridor trade flows © 2026 Lake Group. All rights reserved.","u":"container-services.html"},{"id":"pg:csr:0","t":"CSR & Sustainability","s":"Lake Group is committed to giving back to the communities it serves and operating with minimal environmental impact. Responsible Growth. Lasting Impact. As one of East Africa's largest private employers, Lake Group takes its social and environmental responsibilities seriously. The Group regularly provides support to community development through many of its CSR activities and is one of the leaders among its peers.","u":"csr.html"},{"id":"pg:csr:1","t":"CSR & Sustainability","s":"We believe that business growth and community development go hand in hand, and that our success must translate into tangible benefits for the people and environments in which we operate. Responsible environmental practices Health, orphan care and relief donations Donating medical equipment to maternal wards in Dar es Salaam's municipal hospitals  delivery beds, delivery kits, wheelchairs, stretchers and BP machines  and supporting referral hospitals such as Temeke.","u":"csr.html"},{"id":"pg:csr:2","t":"CSR & Sustainability","s":"Assisting needy children and orphanage centres, supporting places of worship, and providing emergency relief  including food and LPG cooking sets for flood-affected families in Rufiji. Responsible handling, storage and transport of petroleum products across the supply chain, with continuous investment in modern equipment and cleaner operations.","u":"csr.html"},{"id":"pg:csr:3","t":"CSR & Sustainability","s":"4,600+ jobs across 8 countries, with a strong preference for hiring and developing local talent at every level of the organisation. Expanding reliable LPG access for households across East Africa  reducing dependence on charcoal, improving indoor air quality and easing deforestation pressure. Industry-leading safety standards across all divisions. Zero-harm ambition for employees, contractors and the communities we operate in.","u":"csr.html"},{"id":"pg:csr:4","t":"CSR & Sustainability","s":"© 2026 Lake Group. All rights reserved.","u":"csr.html"},{"id":"pg:fleet:0","t":"Our Fleet","s":"Over 700 purpose-built trucks operating 24/7 across East and Central Africa, the backbone of our logistics operations. Heavy-duty tankers for bulk liquid petroleum transport, with capacities from 12,000 to 40,000 litres. Every tanker is GPS-tracked and operated under full regulatory licensing. Versatile flatbed and curtain-side trailers for steel, construction materials, containers and oversized cargo across the region.","u":"fleet.html"},{"id":"pg:fleet:1","t":"Our Fleet","s":"Specialised pressurised tankers for bulk LPG transport between bottling plants and distribution points across East Africa. 20 truck mixers (12m³ each) dedicated to GCCP ready-mix concrete delivery to construction sites across Dar es Salaam. Reach stackers, terminal tractors and container trucks for AFICD inland depot operations in Tanzania, Zambia and Mozambique.","u":"fleet.html"},{"id":"pg:fleet:2","t":"Our Fleet","s":"Support fleet of pickups, service vehicles and supervisor cars for field operations, maintenance and last-mile delivery support. © 2026 Lake Group. All rights reserved.","u":"fleet.html"},{"id":"pg:fuel:0","t":"Fuel & Petroleum","s":"One of Tanzania's top 5 petroleum distributors, supplying quality fuel across 8 countries in East and Central Africa. Lake Oil Ltd. is the flagship company of Lake Group and one of Tanzania's top 5 distributors of petroleum products. Founded in 2006, it has established a strong footprint across all of East and Central Africa. We supply white petroleum products  petrol and diesel  through retail stations, bulk delivery and strategic storage facilities across the region, and provide bunkering services for vessels calling at the port of Dar es Salaam.","u":"fuel.html"},{"id":"pg:fuel:1","t":"Fuel & Petroleum","s":"✓Retail fuel stations, 85+ across Tanzania and the region ✓Bulk petroleum supply for corporate and government clients ✓Own oil storage facilities in Tanzania, Kenya, Burundi and DRC ✓Competitive pricing backed by regional supply chain scale ✓Quality products meeting national and international standards Ranked among the top 5 petroleum distributors in Tanzania by volume.","u":"fuel.html"},{"id":"pg:fuel:2","t":"Fuel & Petroleum","s":"Strategic storage facilities in Tanzania, Kenya, Burundi and DRC. Integrated logistics fleet for reliable, on-time delivery every time. Pan-African fuel supply capability across East and Central Africa. © 2026 Lake Group. All rights reserved.","u":"fuel.html"},{"id":"pg:gallery:0","t":"Gallery","s":"Real photos from our operations, GCCP concrete plant, MERM Dubai, LPG cylinders, fuel operations and more. Lake Group in Action 39 Photos Real photos sourced directly from lakeoilgroup.com, our operations across East Africa and the Middle East. Field Operations across East Africa Largest Petroleum Distributors in Tanzania Fastest Growing Company in Africa","u":"gallery.html"},{"id":"pg:gallery:1","t":"Gallery","s":"Pan-African Supply Chain Operations Quality, Service, Safety, Professionalism Petroleum Products across East Africa Lake Oil Ltd.: Fuel Station Operations Lake Oil Ltd.: Petroleum Supply Operations Lake Gas Ltd.: LPG Distribution across East Africa Lake Gas, 6kg Domestic LPG Cylinder Lake Gas, 15kg Cylinder for Hotels & Restaurants Lake Gas, 38kg Commercial LPG Cylinder","u":"gallery.html"},{"id":"pg:gallery:2","t":"Gallery","s":"Lake Gas, 10kg Composite Cylinder (Non-Explosive, Tran Lake Gas, Composite Cylinder Product Range GCCP, Gulf Concrete Batching Plant, Dar es Salaam GCCP, Sany International Aggregate Plant (250T/hr) GCCP, Ready-Mix Concrete Delivery Operations GCCP, Mixer Truck Fleet (20 units, 12m³ each) GCCP, Concrete Boom Pump (32m) at Construction Site GCCP, Quality Assurance & Testing Laboratory","u":"gallery.html"},{"id":"pg:gallery:3","t":"Gallery","s":"GCCP, Plant Overview, Vijibweni Area GCCP, Heavy Equipment & Sany Batching Systems GCCP, Ready-Mix Supply to Prestige Projects GCCP, Lugoba Quarry Aggregate Production GCCP, Foundation & Piling Concrete Operations GCCP, Truck Mixer Loading at Batching Plant MERM: Middle East Ready Mix LLC, Dubai, UAE MERM: One of Lake Group's Largest Premix Plants","u":"gallery.html"},{"id":"pg:gallery:4","t":"Gallery","s":"MERM: Ready-Mix Concrete Fleet, Dubai MERM: Batching Plant Operations, Dubai MERM: Concrete Supply to UAE Construction Projects MERM: Mixer Truck Fleet at Dubai Plant MERM: Aggregate & Materials Storage, UAE MERM: Quality Control Laboratory, Dubai MERM: Ready-Mix Concrete Production Line, UAE MERM: Lake Group Middle East Operations 39 real photos from Lake Group operations, GCCP, MERM Dubai, Lake Gas, Lake Oil & more.","u":"gallery.html"},{"id":"pg:gallery:5","t":"Gallery","s":"© 2026 Lake Group. All rights reserved.","u":"gallery.html"},{"id":"pg:history:0","t":"Our History","s":"From a single fuel station to a pan-African conglomerate, the journey of Lake Group since 2006. A story of bold decisions, relentless expansion, and building an energy empire from the ground up. Ally Edha Awadh founds Lake Oil Ltd. at age 27 in Dar es Salaam, Tanzania, the seed of what would become Lake Group. Begins petroleum distribution with a small fleet.","u":"history.html"},{"id":"pg:history:1","t":"Our History","s":"Logistics & First Regional Steps Lake Trans Ltd. is established as the Group's logistics arm. The same year, DRC Petroleum S.A.R.L. is founded in the Democratic Republic of Congo and Lake Petroleum Ltd. is incorporated in Zambia  the Group's first ventures beyond Tanzania. Gulf Concrete and Cement Products Company (GCCP) is established, quickly becoming the market leader in ready-mix concrete supply in Dar es Salaam.","u":"history.html"},{"id":"pg:history:2","t":"Our History","s":"Burundi Petroleum opens its first petrol station in Burundi, and Lake Petroleum Rwanda  established in Kigali in 2011  begins importing and distributing fuel across Rwanda. Lubricants & Composite Cylinders Lake Lubes Ltd. is established in Dar es Salaam to blend and market the Group's own lubricants, and Lake Gas launches Africa's first composite LPG cylinders  non-explosive, lightweight and translucent.","u":"history.html"},{"id":"pg:history:3","t":"Our History","s":"The Competition Authority of Kenya approves Lake Oil's acquisition of Hashi Energy's Kenyan fuel-station network  a landmark step into East Africa's largest retail fuel market. Lake Gas invests in Tanga, commissioning what opens as East Africa's largest LPG storage terminal  1,000 MT of capacity, receiving ships through a dedicated single point mooring buoy.","u":"history.html"},{"id":"pg:history:4","t":"Our History","s":"Lake Steel and Allied Products starts operations at Visiga, Kibaha  the first producer of high-strength, corrosion-resistant (HS-CR) rebar in Tanzania, with an annual capacity of 100,000 metric tonnes. The Tanga LPG terminal is expanded to 3,000 MT, and founder Ally Edha Awadh is named Young Business Leader of the Year by the African Leadership Magazine.","u":"history.html"},{"id":"pg:history:5","t":"Our History","s":"4,600+ Employees. 8 Countries. Still Growing. Lake Group continues to expand, deepening its regional footprint, investing in new technologies, and driving economic development across East and Central Africa. Join our team or partner with us across Africa. © 2026 Lake Group. All rights reserved.","u":"history.html"},{"id":"pg:index:0","t":"Home","s":"From our headquarters in Dar es Salaam, Lake Group operates across eight countries  Tanzania, Kenya, Zambia, Rwanda, Burundi, DR Congo, Ethiopia and Mozambique  with a Dubai hub extending the network to global markets. Global PerspectiveA single view of the network that moves energy across East and Central Africa. Our FootprintEight countries served from Dar es Salaam by a fleet of 700+ trucks.","u":"index.html"},{"id":"pg:index:1","t":"Home","s":"On the Ground85+ stations in Tanzania, the Tanga LPG terminal and vessel bunkering at Dar es Salaam port. A Conglomerate Built on Grit and Vision Founded by CEO & Chairman Ally Edha Awadh in 2006 at just 27 years old, Lake Group has grown from a single fuel outlet into one of East and Central Africa's largest energy, logistics and industrial conglomerates.","u":"index.html"},{"id":"pg:index:2","t":"Home","s":"Today, with 4,600+ employees across 21 nationalities, 700+ trucks, 85+ fuel stations and 20+ subsidiaries, Lake Group powers everyday life across Tanzania, Kenya, Zambia, Rwanda, Burundi, DRC, Ethiopia and Mozambique. From fuel stations to steel mills, Lake Group operates across the full energy and industrial value chain of East Africa. Top 5 petroleum distributor in Tanzania. Retail stations, bulk supply and storage across 8 countries.","u":"index.html"},{"id":"pg:index:3","t":"Home","s":"Lake Gas operates LPG bottling and distribution with cylinders for domestic and commercial use across 6 countries. Lake Trans operates 700+ trucks for bulk liquid haulage and regional logistics across East & Central Africa. GCCP, Dar es Salaam's leading ready-mix concrete supplier. 30,000 m³ aggregate monthly from our Lugoba quarry. Lake Lubes manufactures and distributes high-quality automotive, industrial and specialty lubricants in 5 countries.","u":"index.html"},{"id":"pg:index:4","t":"Home","s":"Tanzania's first HS-CR rebar producer. Fully automated rolling mill, 100,000 MT/year capacity. AFICD & ACFS provide inland container depot and freight station services across TZ, ZM and MZ. Operations across Tanzania, Kenya, Zambia, Rwanda, Burundi, DRC, Ethiopia, Mozambique & Dubai. \"Welcome to a diverse pioneer in fuel marketing, haulage, LPG bottling, cylinder manufacturing and concrete production. With experienced engineers and business professionals across our divisions, we are fully geared to meet the demands of the global marketplace.\"","u":"index.html"},{"id":"pg:index:5","t":"Home","s":"CEO & Chairman, Lake Group | Founded Lake Group at age 27 in 2006 Talk to our team about fuel supply, logistics, or any of our services across East Africa. © 2026 Lake Group. All rights reserved.","u":"index.html"},{"id":"pg:investors:0","t":"Investor Relations","s":"Financial highlights, company growth profile and governance information for current and prospective investors. A Track Record of Vertical Growth Lake Group has demonstrated consistent and significant growth since its founding in 2006. From a single petroleum distributor in Dar es Salaam, it has grown into a diversified conglomerate operating across 8 countries with 20+ subsidiaries.","u":"investors.html"},{"id":"pg:investors:1","t":"Investor Relations","s":"Our financial strength, high credit rating in the global business community, and diversified revenue streams across energy, logistics and construction materials make Lake Group a resilient and high-potential investment. The Group is privately held, headquartered in Tanzania, and has a direct economic impact in every market it operates, supporting local employment, supply chains and infrastructure development.","u":"investors.html"},{"id":"pg:investors:2","t":"Investor Relations","s":"Eight distinct business lines across energy, logistics, manufacturing and construction reduce single-sector risk and provide stable multi-stream revenue. Operations across 8 high-growth East and Central African markets, some of the world's fastest-growing economies by GDP and population. From 1 company in 2006 to 20+ subsidiaries, a track record of disciplined expansion and value creation over nearly two decades.","u":"investors.html"},{"id":"pg:investors:3","t":"Investor Relations","s":"Own storage facilities, truck fleet (700+), rolling mill, concrete plants, quarry and container depots, significant hard-asset base. Founded and led by Ally Edha Awadh: an experienced entrepreneur who has built a high-credit-rated organisation over nearly two decades. Active corporate social responsibility across all markets, building brand equity, local goodwill and sustainable business relationships.","u":"investors.html"},{"id":"pg:investors:4","t":"Investor Relations","s":"Interested in Investing or Partnering with Lake Group? Contact our corporate team for further information on the Group's financial profile and partnership opportunities. © 2026 Lake Group. All rights reserved.","u":"investors.html"},{"id":"pg:leadership:0","t":"Leadership","s":"The visionaries and industry professionals driving Lake Group's growth across East and Central Africa. Guided by Experience. Driven by Vision. Our leadership team brings together decades of expertise across energy, logistics, finance and engineering. Founder of Lake Group (2006) · Forbes-recognised entrepreneur · Young Business Leader of the Year, African Leadership Magazine 2022","u":"leadership.html"},{"id":"pg:leadership:1","t":"Leadership","s":"Mr. Awadh established Lake Oil at age 27 and grew it into one of East and Central Africa's largest energy, logistics and industrial conglomerates, operating across Tanzania, Kenya, Zambia, DRC, Burundi, Rwanda, Ethiopia and Mozambique with 4,600+ employees from 21 nationalities. \"With a team of experienced engineers and business professionals across our units, Lake Group is fully geared to meet the demands of the global marketplace, from fuel marketing and haulage to LPG, steel, lubricants and concrete.\"","u":"leadership.html"},{"id":"pg:leadership:2","t":"Leadership","s":"Under his leadership the Group has expanded into Lake Trans, Lake Gas, Lake Lubes, Lake Steel, Gulf Concrete & Cement Products, African Inland Container Depot and regional oil storage and retail networks. In 2023 he was also named Young African Energy Leader of the Year at the African Business Leadership Awards. The executives overseeing Lake Group's day-to-day operations, people and strategic growth.","u":"leadership.html"},{"id":"pg:leadership:3","t":"Leadership","s":"Managing Director · Lake Oil Tanzania Leads Lake Oil's petroleum distribution, retail network and corporate partnerships, representing the flagship company at major industry and community events across Tanzania. Executive Director · Lake Group Oversees Group-wide executive operations and represents Lake Group at CSR initiatives, hospital donations and community outreach programmes across Dar es Salaam.","u":"leadership.html"},{"id":"pg:leadership:4","t":"Leadership","s":"Human Resources Director · Lake Oil Heads people strategy and workforce development for Lake Oil, supporting the Group's diverse team of 4,600+ professionals across East and Central Africa. Manages major Group projects including Lake Agro's greenfield development and coordinates humanitarian relief efforts such as flood-response aid in Rufiji and coastal regions.","u":"leadership.html"},{"id":"pg:leadership:5","t":"Leadership","s":"Each subsidiary is led by sector specialists in oil & gas, logistics, engineering, manufacturing and port services. Flagship petroleum importer, depot operator and retail network  among Tanzania's top five fuel distributors. MD: Abdulrahman Mohamed 700+ truck logistics fleet for petroleum, dry cargo and cross-border haulage across East Africa.","u":"leadership.html"},{"id":"pg:leadership:6","t":"Leadership","s":"LPG bottling, composite cylinders and East Africa's largest LPG storage terminal in Tanga. Lubricant blending plant in Dar es Salaam producing greases and engine oils for regional markets. Steel manufacturing including HS-CR rebars and construction materials for infrastructure projects. Gulf Concrete & Cement Products (GCCP) Ready-mix concrete and aggregates, market leader in Dar es Salaam premix supply.","u":"leadership.html"},{"id":"pg:leadership:7","t":"Leadership","s":"African Inland Container Depot (AFICD) ICD, CFS and empty container depot services with rail-linked logistics in Tanzania. Agricultural and greenfield project development. Projects Manager: Nassoro Abubakari Lake Group's workforce reflects the rich diversity of the African continent, with 4,600+ professionals from 21 nationalities working together toward shared goals.","u":"leadership.html"},{"id":"pg:leadership:8","t":"Leadership","s":"© 2026 Lake Group. All rights reserved.","u":"leadership.html"},{"id":"pg:logistics:0","t":"Transport & Haulage","s":"700+ truck fleet providing bulk liquid transport and regional cargo haulage across East and Central Africa. The Backbone of East Africa's Supply Chain Lake Trans Ltd. is one of East Africa's largest logistics operators, running a fleet of 700+ trucks for bulk liquid haulage, general cargo and regional cross-border transport. From petroleum tankers to dry cargo, our transport division ensures timely, safe and cost-effective delivery to destinations across Tanzania, Kenya and Zambia, and throughout the wider region.","u":"logistics.html"},{"id":"pg:logistics:1","t":"Transport & Haulage","s":"✓Bulk petroleum and liquid haulage ✓Dry cargo and containerised freight ✓Cross-border regional transport ✓Real-time fleet tracking capability ✓Experienced drivers and route managers Purpose-Built for Africa's Roads Specialised bulk liquid tankers for safe petroleum transport, fully compliant with regional hazmat regulations. Heavy-duty flatbed and cargo trucks for construction materials, steel, containers and general freight.","u":"logistics.html"},{"id":"pg:logistics:2","t":"Transport & Haulage","s":"Dedicated LPG transport vehicles for safe cylinder and bulk gas delivery across East Africa. © 2026 Lake Group. All rights reserved.","u":"logistics.html"},{"id":"pg:lpg:0","t":"LPG Gas","s":"Powering homes, restaurants and industry across 7 East African countries with safe, reliable LPG cylinders. Clean Energy for Every Kitchen Lake Gas Ltd. is East Africa's trusted LPG bottling and distribution company, operating across 6 countries. From domestic cooking to large-scale commercial kitchens and industrial applications, Lake Gas provides safe and reliable liquefied petroleum gas.","u":"lpg.html"},{"id":"pg:lpg:1","t":"LPG Gas","s":"Our innovative composite cylinder range, launched in Dar es Salaam, marks a new revolution in cooking gas technology, combining safety with aesthetics. © 2026 Lake Group. All rights reserved.","u":"lpg.html"},{"id":"pg:lubricants:0","t":"Lubricants","s":"High-quality automotive, industrial and specialty lubricants manufactured and distributed across East and Central Africa. Lake Lubes Ltd., established in 2014, manufactures and distributes a comprehensive range of lubricants and greases serving automotive, industrial and specialty applications across East and Central Africa. Our lubricants are formulated to meet international standards, providing superior protection and performance even in Africa's most demanding operating environments.","u":"lubricants.html"},{"id":"pg:lubricants:1","t":"Lubricants","s":"Engine oils, transmission fluids and greases for passenger and commercial vehicles. Heavy-duty industrial oils for machinery, compressors and manufacturing equipment. Gear oils, automatic transmission fluid, radiator coolants, hydraulic oils and lithium greases for specialist applications. Oil analysis, technical advice and maintenance support for corporate fleet customers.","u":"lubricants.html"},{"id":"pg:lubricants:2","t":"Lubricants","s":"© 2026 Lake Group. All rights reserved.","u":"lubricants.html"},{"id":"pg:media_center:0","t":"News","s":"Press releases, official statements, corporate videos and downloadable media assets for Lake Group. Ally Edha Awadh Named Young Business Leader of the Year Lake Group founder and Chairman Ally Edha Awadh received the African Leadership Magazine's 2022 Young Business Leader of the Year award at a ceremony held at the House of Lords in London.","u":"media-center.html"},{"id":"pg:media_center:1","t":"News","s":"Lake Gas Expands Tanga LPG Terminal to 3,000 Metric Tonnes Lake Gas has expanded its Tanga terminal  opened as East Africa's largest LPG storage facility  from 1,000 to 3,000 metric tonnes, strengthening supply to Tanzania and neighbouring markets. Lake Gas Launches Africa's First Composite LPG Cylinders Lake Gas introduced composite LPG cylinders  non-explosive, non-corrosive, lightweight and translucent  at a launch event in Dar es Salaam on 18 June 2014, a first for the African market.","u":"media-center.html"},{"id":"pg:media_center:2","t":"News","s":"For interview requests, press enquiries or media partnerships, please contact our communications team. Monday – Friday, 9:00 – 18:00 EAT © 2026 Lake Group. All rights reserved.","u":"media-center.html"},{"id":"pg:news:0","t":"News","s":"News from across Lake Group  announcements, expansions, product launches and community activities. For press releases, interviews or media partnerships: © 2026 Lake Group. All rights reserved.","u":"news.html"},{"id":"pg:projects:0","t":"Major Projects","s":"A showcase of landmark construction, infrastructure and supply projects delivered by Lake Group across East Africa. Delivering East Africa's Development From multi-million dollar construction projects to long-haul logistics contracts, Lake Group has the scale, expertise and equipment to deliver. Tanga LPG Import Terminal  East Africa's Largest","u":"projects.html"},{"id":"pg:projects:1","t":"Major Projects","s":"Lake Gas built East Africa's largest LPG storage terminal at Tanga  commissioned at 1,000 MT and later expanded to 3,000 MT  with a dedicated single point mooring buoy that lets ships discharge directly to the terminal. Pan-African Petroleum Supply Chain Lake Oil and Lake Trans jointly operate one of East Africa's largest petroleum supply chains, distributing fuel to 8 countries with 700+ trucks running 24/7.","u":"projects.html"},{"id":"pg:projects:2","t":"Major Projects","s":"Lake Steel Rolling Mill, Tanzania First Tanzania's first HS-CR rebar producer. The fully computerised rolling mill at Visiga, Kibaha runs at up to 25 tonnes per hour  100,000 MT annual capacity  and its bars are approved for use in government projects. MERM Ready Mix, Dubai Expansion Middle East Ready Mix LLC (MERM), Lake Group's Dubai-based premix concrete operation, has been producing ready-mix concrete since 2005 and serves major construction projects across Dubai.","u":"projects.html"},{"id":"pg:projects:3","t":"Major Projects","s":"African Inland Container Depot Network AFICD operates strategic inland container depots in Tanzania, Zambia and Mozambique, extending port capacity into the hinterland and enabling efficient cross-border trade. Lake Gas pioneered the introduction of composite LPG cylinders in East Africa, non-explosive, lightweight and translucent, revolutionising domestic cooking gas safety.","u":"projects.html"},{"id":"pg:projects:4","t":"Major Projects","s":"Have a major project that needs energy, logistics or construction supply support? © 2026 Lake Group. All rights reserved.","u":"projects.html"},{"id":"pg:services:0","t":"Services ▾","s":"From fuel stations to steel mills, eight sectors, one vision, across eight countries. Lake Group operates across the full energy and industrial value chain of East and Central Africa. Top 5 petroleum distributor in Tanzania. 85+ retail stations, bulk petroleum supply and storage. Lake Gas LPG bottling and distribution. 6kg, 10kg, 15kg and 38kg cylinders for domestic and commercial use across 6 countries.","u":"services.html"},{"id":"pg:services:1","t":"Services ▾","s":"Lake Trans operates 700+ trucks for bulk liquid haulage and general cargo across East & Central Africa. GCCP, Dar es Salaam's leading ready-mix concrete supplier. 30,000 m³ aggregate monthly. Lake Lubes manufactures and distributes automotive, industrial and specialty lubricants in 5 countries. Tanzania's first HS-CR rebar producer. 100,000 MT/year rolling mill capacity.","u":"services.html"},{"id":"pg:services:2","t":"Services ▾","s":"AFICD & ACFS inland container depot and freight station services across TZ, ZM and MZ. Operations across 8 countries plus Dubai. Interactive map of all Lake Group facilities. Talk to our team about fuel supply, logistics, or any of our services across East Africa. © 2026 Lake Group. All rights reserved.","u":"services.html"},{"id":"pg:station_locator:0","t":"Station Locator","s":"Locate the nearest Lake Oil fuel station and see the services available  Lake Oil stations are open 24 hours. Find your nearest Lake Oil station by city or region. Mikocheni Light Industrial Area, Dar es Salaam Open 24 hours | Petrol, Diesel, LPG Open 24 hours | Petrol, Diesel, Lubricants Mwanza City, Lake Victoria Region Open 24 hours | Petrol, Diesel, Truck Diesel","u":"station-locator.html"},{"id":"pg:station_locator:1","t":"Station Locator","s":"© 2026 Lake Group. All rights reserved. e.g. Dar es Salaam, Arusha, Mwanza...","u":"station-locator.html"},{"id":"pg:steel:0","t":"Lake Steel","s":"Tanzania's first producer of HS-CR reinforcement steel bars. Fully computerised rolling mill with 100,000 MT annual capacity. First in Tanzania. Built to Last. Lake Steel Ltd. is the first company in Tanzania to introduce unique High Strength, Corrosion Resistant (HS-CR) reinforcement steel bars, a game-changer for the East African construction industry.","u":"steel.html"},{"id":"pg:steel:1","t":"Lake Steel","s":"Our state-of-the-art, fully computerised and automatic Steel Rolling Mill plant has a production capacity of up to 25 tonnes per hour, translating to an annual capacity of 100,000 metric tonnes of high-quality steel bars. Our HS-CR bars maintain strength at temperatures up to 600°C, compared to 350°C for ordinary rebars, providing critical fire resistance advantages for major construction projects.","u":"steel.html"},{"id":"pg:steel:2","t":"Lake Steel","s":"Billets tested in our lab. Only approved materials proceed. Billets heated to rolling temperature in our furnace. Computerised rolling at 25T/hr capacity. Quality testing to national and international standards before dispatch. © 2026 Lake Group. All rights reserved.","u":"steel.html"},{"id":"pg:sustainability:0","t":"CSR & Sustainability","s":"Lake Group's commitment to environmental responsibility, clean energy transition and reducing our operational footprint. Energy for Africa. Responsibly. As a major energy and logistics company operating across 8 countries, Lake Group recognises its responsibility to operate in a manner that minimises environmental impact and contributes to sustainable development across Africa.","u":"sustainability.html"},{"id":"pg:sustainability:1","t":"CSR & Sustainability","s":"Our sustainability strategy covers environmental stewardship, clean cooking energy access, land reclamation, waste management and progressive decarbonisation of our logistics fleet. LPG, a core business of Lake Gas, plays a critical role in East Africa's clean cooking agenda, reducing dependence on charcoal and firewood, improving indoor air quality and reducing deforestation.","u":"sustainability.html"},{"id":"pg:sustainability:2","t":"CSR & Sustainability","s":"Lake Gas supplies LPG across 6 countries, helping households switch from charcoal to cleaner cooking. Every cylinder sold reduces CO₂, indoor air pollution and deforestation pressure. Petroleum transport operations are run with a zero-spillage ambition. Tankers are regularly inspected and maintained at the Group's own workshops in Kibaha, Kigamboni and Morogoro.","u":"sustainability.html"},{"id":"pg:sustainability:3","t":"CSR & Sustainability","s":"GCCP's quarry at Lugoba supplies aggregate for the Group's concrete operations. We are committed to responsible extraction and to progressively rehabilitating worked-out areas. Ongoing investment in newer, fuel-efficient trucks, reducing per-kilometre emissions across our 700+ vehicle fleet while improving service reliability. Countries with clean LPG access via Lake Gas","u":"sustainability.html"},{"id":"pg:sustainability:4","t":"CSR & Sustainability","s":"Local jobs created across 8 countries Tolerance for petroleum spillage incidents m³ aggregate monthly, supporting sustainable construction © 2026 Lake Group. All rights reserved.","u":"sustainability.html"}]},"fr":{"docs":[{"id":"fact:countries","t":"Où nous opérons","s":"Lake Group opère dans 8 pays d’Afrique  la Tanzanie (siège), le Kenya, la Zambie, la RD Congo, le Rwanda, le Burundi, l’Éthiopie et le Mozambique  avec aussi une présence aux Émirats arabes unis (Dubaï) via MERM et SAFF.","u":"africa-network.html","k":"pays où opérez opérations présence afrique quels quelles régions implantation","f":1},{"id":"fact:founding","t":"Notre fondation","s":"Lake Group a été fondé en 2006 à Dar es Salaam, en Tanzanie, par Ally Edha Awadh, avec Lake Oil comme société phare. Le groupe est devenu l’un des conglomérats d’énergie et de transport à la croissance la plus rapide d’Afrique de l’Est et centrale.","u":"about.html","k":"fondé fondation quand créé histoire année établi fondateur","f":1},{"id":"fact:leadership","t":"Direction","s":"Ally Edha Awadh est le fondateur, PDG et président de Lake Group. Il a fondé le groupe en 2006, à 27 ans, avec une seule station-service à Dar es Salaam.","u":"leadership.html","k":"pdg président fondateur direction dirigeant qui dirige awadh directeur","f":1},{"id":"fact:contact","t":"Nous contacter","s":"Notre siège : Plot 49, Mikocheni Light Industrial Area, P.O. Box 5055, Dar es Salaam, Tanzanie. Tél : (+255) 222 780 510 ou (+255) 222 780 479. E-mail : admin@lakeoilgroup.com.","u":"contact.html","k":"contact téléphone email adresse siège bureau appeler joindre coordonnées","f":1},{"id":"fact:workforce","t":"Nos équipes","s":"Lake Group emploie plus de 4 600 personnes de 21 nationalités dans l’ensemble de ses opérations.","u":"about.html","k":"employés effectif personnel combien salariés équipe","f":1},{"id":"fact:fleet","t":"Notre flotte","s":"Lake Trans, la branche logistique du groupe fondée en 2008, exploite une flotte de plus de 700 camions  tous suivis par GPS  transportant liquides en vrac et marchandises vers la Zambie, le Rwanda, la RD Congo, le Burundi, le Malawi, le Kenya et l’Ouganda, avec des ateliers à Kibaha, Kigamboni, Morogoro, Nairobi et Ndola.","u":"fleet.html","k":"flotte camions combien véhicules citernes transport lake trans","f":1},{"id":"fact:stations","t":"Stations-service","s":"Lake Group exploite des réseaux de stations-service dans la région : 85 stations en Tanzanie, 40 au Kenya, 25 en Zambie, 16 au Burundi, 10 au Rwanda et 8 en RD Congo. Utilisez le localisateur de stations pour trouver la plus proche.","u":"station-locator.html","k":"stations essence combien où localisateur station-service réseau","f":1},{"id":"fact:lakeoil","t":"Lake Oil  carburants & pétrole","s":"Lake Oil, la société phare du groupe, est l’un des 5 premiers distributeurs de produits pétroliers en Tanzanie. Son dépôt de Kigamboni à Dar es Salaam offre 38 millions de litres de stockage avec un accès direct par pipeline à la jetée d’importation, appuyé par 85 stations en propre et une flotte de 300 camions-citernes.","u":"fuel.html","k":"lake oil carburant pétrole diesel essence dépôt stockage distributeur","f":1},{"id":"fact:lakegas","t":"Lake Gas  GPL","s":"Lake Gas fournit du GPL au détail et en vrac en Tanzanie, Zambie, RD Congo, au Kenya, au Burundi et au Rwanda, avec des bouteilles de 6 kg, 10 kg composite, 15 kg et 38 kg. Premier à introduire les bouteilles GPL composites en Afrique, son terminal de Tanga a été construit comme la plus grande installation de stockage de GPL d’Afrique de l’Est.","u":"lpg.html","k":"gpl gaz bouteilles lake gas cuisine composite tanga vrac","f":1},{"id":"fact:lakesteel","t":"Lake Steel","s":"Lake Steel est la première entreprise de Tanzanie à introduire des barres d’armature haute résistance et anticorrosion (HS-CR). Son laminoir entièrement informatisé à Kibaha produit jusqu’à 25 tonnes par heure  environ 100 000 tonnes par an.","u":"steel.html","k":"acier armature hs-cr barres lake steel laminoir fer","f":1},{"id":"fact:concrete","t":"GCCP  béton & granulats","s":"GCCP (Gulf Concrete & Cement Products), créée en 2010, est le premier fournisseur de béton prêt à l’emploi de Dar es Salaam, avec des centrales à béton entièrement automatiques, sa propre carrière à Lugoba, des pompes à flèche et 20 camions-malaxeurs de 12 m³. Gulf Aggregates exploite les installations de concassage.","u":"concrete.html","k":"béton gccp prêt-à-l’emploi ciment granulats carrière gulf","f":1},{"id":"fact:lubricants","t":"Lake Lubes  lubrifiants","s":"Lake Lubes, immatriculée à Dar es Salaam en 2014, fabrique et distribue lubrifiants et graisses  dont LAKE 4T, LAKE HD SUPREME, LAKE POWER, huiles pour engrenages, ATF, liquides de refroidissement et graisses  vendus via le réseau de stations Lake Oil et dans les pays du groupe, avec une assistance technique 24 h/24.","u":"lubricants.html","k":"lubrifiants huile graisse lake lubes moteur refroidissement","f":1},{"id":"fact:containers","t":"Services de conteneurs","s":"AFICD (African Inland Container Depot) fournit des services ICD, CFS et de dépôt de conteneurs vides à Tazara, Pugu Road, Dar es Salaam  un parc de 14 000 m² d’une capacité de 4 000 EVP relié au port par voie ferrée  au service du Rwanda, du Burundi, de l’Ouganda, de la RD Congo, de la Zambie et du Malawi. ACFS ajoute une gare de fret de 5 000 EVP.","u":"container-services.html","k":"conteneurs icd cfs aficd acfs dépôt evp fret port","f":1},{"id":"fact:subsidiaries","t":"Sociétés du groupe","s":"Les principales sociétés de Lake Group sont Lake Oil (carburants & pétrole), Lake Gas (GPL), Lake Trans (logistique), Lake Lubes (lubrifiants), Lake Steel (armatures HS-CR), GCCP et Gulf Aggregates (béton & granulats), AFICD et ACFS (services de conteneurs), plus MERM (béton prêt à l’emploi) et SAFF (transit) à Dubaï.","u":"services.html","k":"filiales sociétés divisions groupe activités secteurs que faites-vous services","f":1},{"id":"fact:careers","t":"Carrières","s":"Nous recherchons en permanence des talents pour les sociétés de notre groupe dans 8 pays. Consultez la page Carrières pour découvrir les opportunités actuelles et postuler.","u":"careers.html","k":"carrières emplois postes recrutement travailler candidature postuler","f":1},{"id":"fact:values","t":"Valeurs & culture","s":"Les valeurs fondamentales de Lake Group sont le travail d’équipe, la fiabilité, l’intégrité et la satisfaction client, portées par une culture de qualité, de service, de sécurité et de professionnalisme.","u":"about.html","k":"valeurs culture mission vision principes qualité sécurité","f":1},{"id":"pg:hero:0","t":"Accueil","s":"Fondé en 2006 · Dar es Salaam, Tanzanie Propulser l'Afrique de l'Est & centrale L'un des conglomérats d'énergie, de logistique et de construction à la croissance la plus rapide d'Afrique, présent dans 8 pays avec plus de 4 600 employés et plus de 700 camions sur les routes.","u":"index.html"},{"id":"pg:ose:0","t":"À propos","s":"Tout a commencé avec un seul réservoir. À 27 ans, Ally Edha Awadh a ouvert une seule station-service à Dar es Salaam. Pas de flotte, pas de réseau, aucune certitude. Juste la conviction que l'Afrique de l'Est méritait une chaîne d'approvisionnement énergétique plus fiable. Ally Edha Awadh, fondateur et président Lake Trans : transport en vrac en Afrique de l'Est","u":"our-story.html"},{"id":"pg:ose:1","t":"À propos","s":"nous avons apporté une énergie propre à la maison. Lake Gas fournit désormais des bouteilles de GPL dans six pays, remplaçant les foyers à charbon et offrant aux familles une façon plus sûre de cuisiner. huit secteurs, une seule vision Nous avons bâti plus qu'une entreprise pétrolière. GCCP : premier fournisseur de béton prêt à l'emploi de Dar es Salaam","u":"our-story.html"},{"id":"pg:ose:2","t":"À propos","s":"Chaque dépôt, chaque camion, chaque bouteille est géré par des personnes. Plus de 4 600 d'entre elles, de 21 nationalités, dans 8 pays. C'est la partie qu'aucun tableau ne peut saisir. Tanzanie &middot; Kenya &middot; Zambie &middot; Rwanda &middot; Burundi &middot; RDC &middot; Éthiopie &middot; Mozambique Qualité. Service. Sécurité. Professionnalisme. Propulser l'Afrique de l'Est et centrale depuis 2006.","u":"our-story.html"},{"id":"pg:ose:3","t":"À propos","s":"« D'une seule station-service à l'un des plus grands conglomérats d'énergie et industriels d'Afrique de l'Est. »","u":"our-story.html"},{"id":"pg:about:0","t":"À propos","s":"L'un des conglomérats de négoce d'énergie et de transport à la croissance la plus rapide d'Afrique de l'Est et centrale, fondé en 2006. D'une simple société pétrolière à une puissance régionale Lake Group a été fondé par son PDG et président M. Ally Edha Awadh en 2006 avec l'ouverture de sa société phare, Lake Oil : un début modeste à Dar es Salaam, en Tanzanie.","u":"about.html"},{"id":"pg:about:1","t":"À propos","s":"Depuis sa création, la croissance de Lake Group a été verticale, devenant l'un des conglomérats de négoce d'énergie, de logistique et de matériaux de construction à la croissance la plus rapide d'Afrique de l'Est et centrale et du Moyen-Orient. Aujourd'hui, Lake Group distribue des produits pétroliers dans 8 pays, possède des installations de stockage dans toute la région, fabrique des lubrifiants et du béton prêt à l'emploi, et exploite une flotte de plus de 700 camions.","u":"about.html"},{"id":"pg:about:2","t":"À propos","s":"Avec un mélange diversifié de 21 nationalités et un effectif total de plus de 4 600 employés, Lake Group continue de croître avec détermination. Fournir aux clients des produits et services de qualité de manière sûre, efficace et économique sans nuire à l'environnement, en identifiant et en investissant de nouveaux secteurs d'activité tout en créant un environnement de travail où les employés dépassent leurs propres limites.","u":"about.html"},{"id":"pg:about:3","t":"À propos","s":"Guidés par nos valeurs fondamentales : esprit d'équipe, fiabilité, intégrité et satisfaction client. Esprit d'équipe, fiabilité, intégrité Devenir le principal détaillant et distributeur régional de produits et services de proximité, en assurant une amélioration continue grâce à l'excellence opérationnelle, à l'innovation et à une culture axée sur la performance.","u":"about.html"},{"id":"pg:about:4","t":"À propos","s":"Aucun compromis sur la qualité La sécurité passe toujours avant tout Une culture que nous chérissons A fondé Lake Group à 27 ans en 2006 « Bienvenue chez un pionnier diversifié de la commercialisation de carburant, du transport, de l'embouteillage de GPL, de la fabrication de bouteilles et de la production de béton. Avec notre équipe expérimentée dans toutes nos unités d'affaires, nous sommes pleinement équipés pour répondre aux exigences du marché mondial. »","u":"about.html"},{"id":"pg:about:5","t":"À propos","s":"Sous la direction de M. Awadh, Lake Group s'est solidement implanté dans le pétrole et le gaz, l'ingénierie, les fournitures industrielles, les projets, le fret, la distribution, le commerce général, le stockage, les solutions béton et le secteur de la construction, bâtissant une organisation hautement solvable depuis près de deux décennies.","u":"about.html"},{"id":"pg:about:6","t":"À propos","s":"© 2026 Lake Group. Tous droits réservés.","u":"about.html"},{"id":"pg:africa_network:0","t":"Carte des opérations en Afrique","s":"Réseau d'opérations en Afrique Carte interactive de la présence de Lake Group dans 8 pays d'Afrique de l'Est et centrale, ainsi qu'à Dubaï. 85+ stations-service, bleu, blanc, jaune et rouge 700+ camions · 4 600+ employés Présent dans tous les coins de l'Afrique de l'Est et centrale Lake Group est géographiquement présent dans toutes les régions de Tanzanie et des pays voisins (Zambie, RDC, Burundi, Rwanda et Kenya), avec des opérations en Éthiopie, au Mozambique et une importante centrale à béton à Dubaï.","u":"africa-network.html"},{"id":"pg:africa_network:1","t":"Carte des opérations en Afrique","s":"Nos stations-service sont immédiatement reconnaissables en bleu, blanc, jaune et rouge accrocheurs, les mêmes couleurs audacieuses de Lake Group que vous verrez sur la carte ci-dessous. bleu, blanc, jaune et rouge accrocheurs Lake Oil Ltd. : Distribution de pétrole Lake Trans Ltd. : Transport et acheminement Lake Gas Ltd. : Embouteillage et distribution de GPL","u":"africa-network.html"},{"id":"pg:africa_network:2","t":"Carte des opérations en Afrique","s":"Lake Lubes Ltd. : Fabrication de lubrifiants Lake Steel Ltd. : Laminoir d'acier HS-CR GCCP Co. Ltd. : Béton prêt à l'emploi AFICD : Dépôt intérieur de conteneurs africain ACFS : Gare de fret pour conteneurs SAFF : Transit et expédition de fret Gulf Aggregate : concassage de pierre Lake Gas Ltd. : Distribution de GPL AFICD : dépôt de conteneurs intérieur","u":"africa-network.html"},{"id":"pg:africa_network:3","t":"Carte des opérations en Afrique","s":"MERM : Middle East Ready Mix LLC L'une des plus grandes activités de béton prêt à l'emploi du Groupe Lake, au service de grands projets de construction à Dubaï. Frontières des pays en blanc · Pays Lake Group en or · Points colorés = infrastructure Pourquoi Lake Group se distingue en Afrique Les mêmes principes qui animent notre page d'accueil, qualité, service, sécurité et professionnalisme, guident chaque marché où nous opérons.","u":"africa-network.html"},{"id":"pg:africa_network:4","t":"Carte des opérations en Afrique","s":"Aucun compromis sur la qualité, du carburant et du GPL à l'acier, aux lubrifiants et au béton prêt à l'emploi. Les normes de service les plus élevées et un approvisionnement constant en carburant et un service client dans chaque territoire. La sécurité est notre priorité dans tout ce que nous faisons : dépôts, flottes de transport, terminaux GPL et chantiers de construction.","u":"africa-network.html"},{"id":"pg:africa_network:5","t":"Carte des opérations en Afrique","s":"Le professionnalisme est la culture que nous chérissons : plus de 4 600 employés de 21 nationalités, une seule équipe. Opérations à travers le continent Dépôts de carburant, terminaux GPL, flottes de camions, dépôts de conteneurs et centrales à béton, tous connectés via notre réseau africain. © 2026 Lake Group. Tous droits réservés.","u":"africa-network.html"},{"id":"pg:careers:0","t":"Carrières","s":"Nous recherchons toujours des professionnels talentueux et motivés pour rejoindre notre équipe en pleine croissance en Afrique de l'Est et centrale. Construisez votre carrière à travers l'Afrique Lake Group offre des carrières à fort impact : vous travaillerez au sein de l'une des entreprises les plus dynamiques d'Afrique de l'Est, avec de réelles opportunités de progresser, de diriger et de faire la différence.","u":"careers.html"},{"id":"pg:careers:1","t":"Carrières","s":"Avec plus de 4 600 employés dans 8 pays et 21 nationalités, nous sommes une équipe véritablement panafricaine unie par des valeurs communes : qualité, service, sécurité et professionnalisme. Opportunités d'évolution entre pays et divisions Travaillez sur des projets qui façonnent le développement de l'Afrique de l'Est Travaillez aux côtés de 21 nationalités dans 8 pays","u":"careers.html"},{"id":"pg:careers:2","t":"Carrières","s":"Des normes de sécurité de pointe dans toutes les opérations Dépôts, terminaux et usines du Groupe Même si aucun poste spécifique ne correspond à votre profil, nous accueillons les candidatures spontanées de professionnels talentueux. © 2026 Lake Group. Tous droits réservés. Parlez-nous de vous et de ce que vous apportez à Lake Group...","u":"careers.html"},{"id":"pg:concrete:0","t":"Béton et granulats","s":"Béton prêt à l'emploi et granulats Gulf Concrete and Cement Products, fournisseur leader du marché du béton prêt à l'emploi à Dar es Salaam depuis 2010. Construire l'avenir de l'Afrique de l'Est Gulf Concrete and Cement Products Company Ltd (GCCP), créée en 2010, est l'un des principaux fournisseurs de béton prêt à l'emploi à Dar es Salaam, impliquée dans nombre des projets de construction les plus prestigieux de la ville.","u":"concrete.html"},{"id":"pg:concrete:1","t":"Béton et granulats","s":"GCCP exploite sa propre carrière à Lugoba avec deux installations de granulats d'une capacité de 250 tonnes/heure chacune, produisant 30 000 m³ de granulats par mois. Ses opérations de béton prêt à l'emploi sont assurées par des centrales Sany International en provenance de Chine. À Dubaï, Lake Group exploite MERM (Middle East Ready Mix LLC), l'une des plus grandes centrales à béton de la région.","u":"concrete.html"},{"id":"pg:concrete:2","t":"Béton et granulats","s":"MERM (Middle East Ready Mix LLC) Capacité de l'installation de granulats ✓Centrales à béton entièrement automatiques Sany International ✓2 installations de concassage de granulats (250 t/h chacune) ✓4 pompes à béton stationnaires (Sany International) ✓2 pompes à flèche (flèche de 32 m) ✓Carrière propre à Lugoba, Tanzanie Portefeuille de béton spécialisé","u":"concrete.html"},{"id":"pg:concrete:3","t":"Béton et granulats","s":"Béton à durcissement ultra-rapide Pour les projets nécessitant un décoffrage rapide et des délais de construction accélérés. Béton résistant à la fissuration Formulation à faible retrait pour dalles, revêtements et structures où le contrôle des fissures est essentiel. S'écoule et se consolide sous son propre poids, idéal pour les armatures denses.","u":"concrete.html"},{"id":"pg:concrete:4","t":"Béton et granulats","s":"Béton à finition soignée pour façades, surfaces décoratives et éléments structurels apparents. Béton perméable pour un drainage durable dans les parkings, routes et aménagements paysagers. Béton pour pieux et fondations Béton haute résistance et très durable pour pieux, fondations profondes et structures critiques. © 2026 Lake Group. Tous droits réservés.","u":"concrete.html"},{"id":"pg:contact:0","t":"Contact","s":"Contactez notre équipe pour toute demande, partenariat, devis ou information sur Lake Group et ses filiales. Nous sommes heureux de vous entendre Plot 49, Mikocheni Light Industrial Area B.P. 5055, Dar es Salaam, Tanzanie 9h00 - 18h00 (heure de l'Afrique de l'Est) Mikocheni, Dar es Salaam, Tanzanie Coordonnées : -6,762806, 39,241447 © 2026 Lake Group. Tous droits réservés.","u":"contact.html"},{"id":"pg:contact:1","t":"Contact","s":"Comment pouvons-nous vous aider ?","u":"contact.html"},{"id":"pg:container_services:0","t":"Services de conteneurs","s":"Services de conteneurs et de dépôt Dépôt intérieur de conteneurs africain (AFICD) et gare de fret pour conteneurs (ACFS), solutions d'extension portuaire en Afrique de l'Est. Services d'extension portuaire La porte d'entrée intérieure du commerce d'Afrique de l'Est AFICD (African Inland Container Depot) et ACFS (African Container Freight Station) sont les bras logistiques portuaires de Lake Group, fournissant des services essentiels de stockage, de manutention et de dédouanement de conteneurs qui étendent la capacité portuaire vers l'arrière-pays.","u":"container-services.html"},{"id":"pg:container_services:1","t":"Services de conteneurs","s":"Avec des opérations en Tanzanie, en Zambie et au Mozambique, nos services de conteneurs sont positionnés sur des corridors stratégiques pour servir les importateurs, exportateurs et compagnies maritimes régionaux. ✓Stockage et empilage de conteneurs ✓Empotage et dépotage de conteneurs (LCL/FCL) ✓Soutien à l'inspection douanière et au dédouanement","u":"container-services.html"},{"id":"pg:container_services:2","t":"Services de conteneurs","s":"✓Manutention de conteneurs frigorifiques ✓Réparation et entretien de conteneurs ✓Intégration avec le réseau de camionnage Lake Trans Dar es Salaam, porte d'entrée de la plus grande économie d'Afrique de l'Est Dépôt intérieur desservant le corridor Zambie-Tanzanie Logistique portuaire stratégique pour les flux commerciaux du corridor de Beira © 2026 Lake Group. Tous droits réservés.","u":"container-services.html"},{"id":"pg:csr:0","t":"RSE et durabilité","s":"Responsabilité de l'entreprise Lake Group s'engage à redonner aux communautés qu'il sert et à opérer avec un impact environnemental minimal. Croissance responsable. Impact durable. En tant que l'un des plus grands employeurs privés d'Afrique de l'Est, Lake Group prend au sérieux ses responsabilités sociales et environnementales. Le Groupe soutient régulièrement le développement communautaire à travers de nombreuses activités de RSE et figure parmi les leaders de son secteur.","u":"csr.html"},{"id":"pg:csr:1","t":"RSE et durabilité","s":"Nous croyons que la croissance des affaires et le développement communautaire vont de pair, et que notre succès doit se traduire par des avantages tangibles pour les personnes et les environnements dans lesquels nous opérons. Pratiques environnementales responsables Dons pour la santé, les orphelins et les secours Don d'équipements médicaux aux maternités des hôpitaux municipaux de Dar es Salaam  lits d'accouchement, kits d'accouchement, fauteuils roulants, brancards et tensiomètres  et soutien aux hôpitaux de référence comme Temeke.","u":"csr.html"},{"id":"pg:csr:2","t":"RSE et durabilité","s":"Enfance et bien-être communautaire Aide aux enfants démunis et aux orphelinats, soutien aux lieux de culte et secours d'urgence  notamment des vivres et des kits de cuisson au GPL pour les familles touchées par les inondations à Rufiji. Manipulation, stockage et transport responsables des produits pétroliers tout au long de la chaîne d'approvisionnement, avec un investissement continu dans des équipements modernes et des opérations plus propres.","u":"csr.html"},{"id":"pg:csr:3","t":"RSE et durabilité","s":"Plus de 4 600 emplois dans 8 pays, avec une forte préférence pour le recrutement et le développement des talents locaux à tous les niveaux de l'organisation. Élargir l'accès fiable au GPL pour les ménages d'Afrique de l'Est  réduire la dépendance au charbon de bois, améliorer la qualité de l'air intérieur et alléger la pression de déforestation.","u":"csr.html"},{"id":"pg:csr:4","t":"RSE et durabilité","s":"Des normes de sécurité de pointe dans toutes les divisions. Une ambition de zéro accident pour les employés, les sous-traitants et les communautés où nous opérons. © 2026 Lake Group. Tous droits réservés.","u":"csr.html"},{"id":"pg:fleet:0","t":"Notre flotte","s":"Plus de 700 camions spécialement conçus fonctionnant 24h/24 en Afrique de l'Est et centrale, l'épine dorsale de nos opérations logistiques. Camions-citernes robustes pour le transport de produits pétroliers en vrac, d'une capacité de 12 000 à 40 000 litres. Chaque citerne est suivie par GPS et exploitée avec toutes les licences réglementaires.","u":"fleet.html"},{"id":"pg:fleet:1","t":"Notre flotte","s":"Remorques plateaux et à rideaux coulissants polyvalentes pour l'acier, les matériaux de construction, les conteneurs et le fret hors normes dans la région. Camions-citernes pressurisés spécialisés pour le transport de GPL en vrac entre les usines d'embouteillage et les points de distribution en Afrique de l'Est. Livraison en vrac et en bouteilles","u":"fleet.html"},{"id":"pg:fleet:2","t":"Notre flotte","s":"20 camions-toupies (12 m³ chacun) dédiés à la livraison de béton prêt à l'emploi GCCP sur les chantiers de Dar es Salaam. Chariots cavaliers, tracteurs de terminal et camions à conteneurs pour les opérations de dépôt intérieur AFICD en Tanzanie, en Zambie et au Mozambique. Flotte de soutien de pick-up, véhicules de service et voitures de supervision pour les opérations sur le terrain, la maintenance et le soutien à la livraison du dernier kilomètre.","u":"fleet.html"},{"id":"pg:fleet:3","t":"Notre flotte","s":"© 2026 Lake Group. Tous droits réservés.","u":"fleet.html"},{"id":"pg:fuel:0","t":"Carburant et pétrole","s":"Distribution de carburant et de pétrole L'un des 5 plus grands distributeurs de pétrole en Tanzanie, fournissant un carburant de qualité dans 8 pays d'Afrique de l'Est et centrale. Lake Oil Ltd. est la société phare de Lake Group et l'un des 5 plus grands distributeurs de produits pétroliers de Tanzanie. Fondée en 2006, elle s'est solidement implantée dans toute l'Afrique de l'Est et centrale.","u":"fuel.html"},{"id":"pg:fuel:1","t":"Carburant et pétrole","s":"Nous fournissons des produits pétroliers blancs  essence et diesel  via des stations-service, la livraison en vrac et des installations de stockage stratégiques dans toute la région, et assurons des services de soutage pour les navires faisant escale au port de Dar es Salaam. ✓Plus de 85 stations-service en Tanzanie et dans la région ✓Approvisionnement en pétrole en vrac pour les clients corporatifs et gouvernementaux","u":"fuel.html"},{"id":"pg:fuel:2","t":"Carburant et pétrole","s":"✓Installations de stockage propres en Tanzanie, au Kenya, au Burundi et en RDC ✓Tarifs compétitifs soutenus par l'envergure régionale de la chaîne d'approvisionnement ✓Produits de qualité conformes aux normes nationales et internationales Classé parmi les 5 premiers distributeurs de pétrole en Tanzanie par volume. Installations de stockage stratégiques en Tanzanie, au Kenya, au Burundi et en RDC.","u":"fuel.html"},{"id":"pg:fuel:3","t":"Carburant et pétrole","s":"Flotte logistique intégrée pour une livraison fiable et ponctuelle à chaque fois. Capacité d'approvisionnement en carburant panafricaine en Afrique de l'Est et centrale. © 2026 Lake Group. Tous droits réservés.","u":"fuel.html"},{"id":"pg:gallery:0","t":"Galerie","s":"Photos réelles de nos opérations, de la centrale à béton GCCP, de MERM Dubaï, des bouteilles GPL, des opérations de carburant et plus encore. Lake Group en action 39 photos Photos réelles provenant directement de lakeoilgroup.com, de nos opérations en Afrique de l'Est et au Moyen-Orient. Opérations sur le terrain en Afrique de l'Est Normes de service les plus élevées","u":"gallery.html"},{"id":"pg:gallery:1","t":"Galerie","s":"Plus grands distributeurs de pétrole en Tanzanie Entreprise à la croissance la plus rapide d'Afrique Opérations de chaîne d'approvisionnement panafricaine Réseau de distribution de carburant 8 pays, plus de 4 600 employés Qualité, service, sécurité, professionnalisme Produits pétroliers en Afrique de l'Est Lake Oil Ltd. : Exploitation de stations-service","u":"gallery.html"},{"id":"pg:gallery:2","t":"Galerie","s":"Lake Oil Ltd. : Opérations d'approvisionnement en pétrole Lake Gas Ltd. : Distribution de GPL en Afrique de l'Est Lake Gas, bouteille GPL domestique de 6 kg Lake Gas, bouteille de 15 kg pour hôtels et restaurants Lake Gas, bouteille GPL commerciale de 38 kg Lake Gas, bouteille composite de 10 kg (non explosive, tran Lake Gas, gamme de bouteilles composites","u":"gallery.html"},{"id":"pg:gallery:3","t":"Galerie","s":"GCCP, centrale à béton Gulf, Dar es Salaam GCCP, installation de granulats Sany International (250 t/h) GCCP, opérations de livraison de béton prêt à l'emploi GCCP, flotte de camions-toupies (20 unités, 12 m³ chacune) GCCP, pompe à béton à flèche (32 m) sur un chantier GCCP, laboratoire d'assurance qualité et d'essais GCCP, vue d'ensemble de l'usine, zone de Vijibweni","u":"gallery.html"},{"id":"pg:gallery:4","t":"Galerie","s":"GCCP, équipements lourds et systèmes de dosage Sany GCCP, approvisionnement en béton pour projets prestigieux GCCP, production de granulats à la carrière de Lugoba GCCP, opérations de béton pour fondations et pieux GCCP, chargement de camion-toupie à la centrale MERM : Middle East Ready Mix LLC, Dubaï, EAU MERM : l'une des plus grandes centrales à béton du Groupe Lake","u":"gallery.html"},{"id":"pg:gallery:5","t":"Galerie","s":"MERM : Flotte de béton prêt à l'emploi, Dubaï MERM : Opérations de centrale à béton, Dubaï MERM : Approvisionnement en béton pour les projets de construction aux EAU MERM : Flotte de camions-toupies à l'usine de Dubaï MERM : Stockage de granulats et matériaux, EAU MERM : Laboratoire de contrôle qualité, Dubaï MERM : Ligne de production de béton prêt à l'emploi, EAU","u":"gallery.html"},{"id":"pg:gallery:6","t":"Galerie","s":"MERM : Opérations de Lake Group au Moyen-Orient 39 photos réelles des opérations de Lake Group, GCCP, MERM Dubaï, Lake Gas, Lake Oil et plus encore. © 2026 Lake Group. Tous droits réservés.","u":"gallery.html"},{"id":"pg:history:0","t":"Notre histoire","s":"D'une seule station-service à un conglomérat panafricain : le parcours de Lake Group depuis 2006. Une histoire de décisions audacieuses, d'expansion incessante et de construction d'un empire énergétique à partir de rien. Ally Edha Awadh fonde Lake Oil Ltd. à 27 ans à Dar es Salaam, en Tanzanie, la graine de ce qui deviendrait Lake Group. Débute la distribution de pétrole avec une petite flotte.","u":"history.html"},{"id":"pg:history:1","t":"Notre histoire","s":"Logistique et premiers pas régionaux Lake Trans Ltd. est créée comme branche logistique du Groupe. La même année, DRC Petroleum S.A.R.L. est fondée en République démocratique du Congo et Lake Petroleum Ltd. est constituée en Zambie  les premières implantations du Groupe hors de Tanzanie. Gulf Concrete and Cement Products Company (GCCP) est créée, devenant rapidement le leader du marché du béton prêt à l'emploi à Dar es Salaam.","u":"history.html"},{"id":"pg:history:2","t":"Notre histoire","s":"L'empreinte est-africaine s'étend Burundi Petroleum ouvre sa première station-service au Burundi, et Lake Petroleum Rwanda  créée à Kigali en 2011  commence à importer et distribuer du carburant à travers le Rwanda. Lubrifiants et bouteilles composites Lake Lubes Ltd. est créée à Dar es Salaam pour formuler et commercialiser les lubrifiants du Groupe, et Lake Gas lance les premières bouteilles de GPL composites d'Afrique  non explosives, légères et translucides.","u":"history.html"},{"id":"pg:history:3","t":"Notre histoire","s":"Entrée à grande échelle au Kenya L'Autorité de la concurrence du Kenya approuve l'acquisition par Lake Oil du réseau de stations-service kenyan de Hashi Energy  une étape majeure sur le plus grand marché de détail de carburant d'Afrique de l'Est. Lake Gas investit à Tanga et met en service ce qui devient à son ouverture le plus grand terminal de stockage de GPL d'Afrique de l'Est  1 000 tonnes de capacité, recevant les navires via une bouée d'amarrage dédiée.","u":"history.html"},{"id":"pg:history:4","t":"Notre histoire","s":"Lake Steel démarre sa production Lake Steel and Allied Products démarre ses activités à Visiga, Kibaha  premier producteur de barres d'armature à haute résistance et anticorrosion (HS-CR) en Tanzanie, avec une capacité annuelle de 100 000 tonnes. Reconnaissance et expansion du GPL Le terminal GPL de Tanga est porté à 3 000 tonnes, et le fondateur Ally Edha Awadh est nommé Jeune dirigeant d'entreprise de l'année par l'African Leadership Magazine.","u":"history.html"},{"id":"pg:history:5","t":"Notre histoire","s":"Plus de 4 600 employés. 8 pays. Toujours en croissance. Lake Group continue de se développer, renforçant son empreinte régionale, investissant dans de nouvelles technologies et stimulant le développement économique en Afrique de l'Est et centrale. Faites partie du prochain chapitre Rejoignez notre équipe ou devenez partenaire à travers l'Afrique.","u":"history.html"},{"id":"pg:history:6","t":"Notre histoire","s":"© 2026 Lake Group. Tous droits réservés.","u":"history.html"},{"id":"pg:index:0","t":"Accueil","s":"Embouteillage et distribution de GPL Services de dépôt de conteneurs Depuis son siège de Dar es Salaam, Lake Group opère dans huit pays  Tanzanie, Kenya, Zambie, Rwanda, Burundi, RD Congo, Éthiopie et Mozambique  avec un hub à Dubaï qui relie le réseau aux marchés mondiaux. Perspective globaleUne vue d'ensemble du réseau qui achemine l'énergie en Afrique de l'Est et centrale.","u":"index.html"},{"id":"pg:index:1","t":"Accueil","s":"Notre empreinteHuit pays desservis depuis Dar es Salaam par une flotte de plus de 700 camions. Sur le terrainPlus de 85 stations en Tanzanie, le terminal GPL de Tanga et le soutage des navires au port de Dar es Salaam. Un conglomérat bâti sur la détermination et la vision Fondé par le PDG et président Ally Edha Awadh en 2006, à seulement 27 ans, Lake Group est passé d'une seule station-service à l'un des plus grands conglomérats d'énergie, de logistique et industriels d'Afrique de l'Est et centrale.","u":"index.html"},{"id":"pg:index:2","t":"Accueil","s":"Aujourd'hui, avec plus de 4 600 employés de 21 nationalités, plus de 700 camions, plus de 85 stations-service et plus de 20 filiales, Lake Group alimente la vie quotidienne en Tanzanie, au Kenya, en Zambie, au Rwanda, au Burundi, en RDC, en Éthiopie et au Mozambique. Huit secteurs. Une seule vision. Des stations-service aux aciéries, Lake Group est présent sur toute la chaîne de valeur énergétique et industrielle de l'Afrique de l'Est.","u":"index.html"},{"id":"pg:index:3","t":"Accueil","s":"Top 5 des distributeurs de pétrole en Tanzanie. Stations-service, approvisionnement en vrac et stockage dans 8 pays. Lake Gas assure l'embouteillage et la distribution de GPL avec des bouteilles à usage domestique et commercial dans 6 pays. Lake Trans exploite plus de 700 camions pour le transport de liquides en vrac et la logistique régionale en Afrique de l'Est et centrale.","u":"index.html"},{"id":"pg:index:4","t":"Accueil","s":"GCCP, le principal fournisseur de béton prêt à l'emploi de Dar es Salaam. 30 000 m³ de granulats par mois depuis notre carrière de Lugoba. Lake Lubes fabrique et distribue des lubrifiants automobiles, industriels et spécialisés de haute qualité dans 5 pays. Premier producteur de barres d'armature HS-CR en Tanzanie. Laminoir entièrement automatisé, capacité de 100 000 t/an.","u":"index.html"},{"id":"pg:index:5","t":"Accueil","s":"AFICD et ACFS fournissent des services de dépôt de conteneurs intérieur et de gare de fret en Tanzanie, en Zambie et au Mozambique. Opérations en Tanzanie, au Kenya, en Zambie, au Rwanda, au Burundi, en RDC, en Éthiopie, au Mozambique et à Dubaï. « Bienvenue chez un pionnier diversifié de la commercialisation de carburant, du transport, de l'embouteillage de GPL, de la fabrication de bouteilles et de la production de béton. Avec des ingénieurs expérimentés et des professionnels dans toutes nos divisions, nous sommes pleinement équipés pour répondre aux exigences du marché mondial. »","u":"index.html"},{"id":"pg:index:6","t":"Accueil","s":"PDG et président, Lake Group | A fondé Lake Group à 27 ans en 2006 Parlez à notre équipe de l'approvisionnement en carburant, de la logistique ou de l'un de nos services en Afrique de l'Est. © 2026 Lake Group. Tous droits réservés.","u":"index.html"},{"id":"pg:investors:0","t":"Relations investisseurs","s":"Faits saillants financiers, profil de croissance de l'entreprise et informations de gouvernance pour les investisseurs actuels et potentiels. Un parcours de croissance verticale Lake Group a démontré une croissance constante et significative depuis sa création en 2006. D'un seul distributeur de pétrole à Dar es Salaam, il est devenu un conglomérat diversifié présent dans 8 pays avec plus de 20 filiales.","u":"investors.html"},{"id":"pg:investors:1","t":"Relations investisseurs","s":"Notre solidité financière, notre excellente notation de crédit dans la communauté commerciale mondiale et nos sources de revenus diversifiées dans l'énergie, la logistique et les matériaux de construction font de Lake Group un investissement résilient à fort potentiel. Le Groupe est une entreprise privée, basée en Tanzanie, qui a un impact économique direct sur chaque marché où il opère, soutenant l'emploi local, les chaînes d'approvisionnement et le développement des infrastructures.","u":"investors.html"},{"id":"pg:investors:2","t":"Relations investisseurs","s":"Huit secteurs d'activité distincts dans l'énergie, la logistique, la fabrication et la construction réduisent le risque sectoriel unique et assurent des revenus stables et diversifiés. Opérations dans 8 marchés à forte croissance d'Afrique de l'Est et centrale, parmi les économies à la croissance la plus rapide au monde en termes de PIB et de population.","u":"investors.html"},{"id":"pg:investors:3","t":"Relations investisseurs","s":"D'une seule société en 2006 à plus de 20 filiales : un historique d'expansion disciplinée et de création de valeur sur près de deux décennies. Installations de stockage propres, flotte de camions (plus de 700), laminoir, centrales à béton, carrière et dépôts de conteneurs : une base d'actifs corporels importante. Fondé et dirigé par Ally Edha Awadh : un entrepreneur expérimenté qui a bâti une organisation hautement solvable depuis près de deux décennies.","u":"investors.html"},{"id":"pg:investors:4","t":"Relations investisseurs","s":"Une responsabilité sociale active sur tous les marchés, renforçant la notoriété de la marque, la bonne volonté locale et des relations d'affaires durables. Intéressé à investir ou à devenir partenaire de Lake Group ? Contactez notre équipe d'entreprise pour plus d'informations sur le profil financier du Groupe et les opportunités de partenariat.","u":"investors.html"},{"id":"pg:investors:5","t":"Relations investisseurs","s":"© 2026 Lake Group. Tous droits réservés.","u":"investors.html"},{"id":"pg:leadership:0","t":"Direction","s":"Les visionnaires et professionnels du secteur qui propulsent la croissance de Lake Group en Afrique de l'Est et centrale. Guidés par l'expérience. Animés par la vision. Notre équipe de direction réunit des décennies d'expertise dans l'énergie, la logistique, la finance et l'ingénierie. Fondateur de Lake Group (2006) · Entrepreneur reconnu par Forbes · Jeune dirigeant d'entreprise de l'année, African Leadership Magazine 2022","u":"leadership.html"},{"id":"pg:leadership:1","t":"Direction","s":"M. Awadh a fondé Lake Oil à 27 ans et en a fait l'un des plus grands conglomérats d'énergie, de logistique et industriels d'Afrique de l'Est et centrale, présent en Tanzanie, au Kenya, en Zambie, en RDC, au Burundi, au Rwanda, en Éthiopie et au Mozambique, avec plus de 4 600 employés de 21 nationalités. « Avec une équipe d'ingénieurs expérimentés et de professionnels dans toutes nos unités, Lake Group est pleinement équipé pour répondre aux exigences du marché mondial, de la commercialisation de carburant et du transport au GPL, à l'acier, aux lubrifiants et au béton. »","u":"leadership.html"},{"id":"pg:leadership:2","t":"Direction","s":"Sous sa direction, le Groupe s'est étendu à Lake Trans, Lake Gas, Lake Lubes, Lake Steel, Gulf Concrete & Cement Products, African Inland Container Depot ainsi qu'à des réseaux régionaux de stockage et de distribution de carburant. En 2023, il a également été nommé Jeune leader africain de l'énergie de l'année aux African Business Leadership Awards.","u":"leadership.html"},{"id":"pg:leadership:3","t":"Direction","s":"Direction du groupe et de Lake Oil Les dirigeants supervisant les opérations quotidiennes, le personnel et la croissance stratégique de Lake Group. Directeur général · Lake Oil Tanzanie Dirige la distribution de pétrole, le réseau de détail et les partenariats d'entreprise de Lake Oil, représentant la société phare lors d'événements industriels et communautaires majeurs en Tanzanie.","u":"leadership.html"},{"id":"pg:leadership:4","t":"Direction","s":"Directeur exécutif · Lake Group Supervise les opérations exécutives à l'échelle du Groupe et représente Lake Group lors d'initiatives RSE, de dons hospitaliers et de programmes communautaires à Dar es Salaam. Directrice des ressources humaines · Lake Oil Dirige la stratégie RH et le développement des effectifs pour Lake Oil, soutenant l'équipe diversifiée de plus de 4 600 professionnels du Groupe en Afrique de l'Est et centrale.","u":"leadership.html"},{"id":"pg:leadership:5","t":"Direction","s":"Gère les grands projets du Groupe, notamment le développement de terrains vierges de Lake Agro, et coordonne les efforts d'aide humanitaire tels que l'aide en réponse aux inondations à Rufiji et dans les régions côtières. Chaque filiale est dirigée par des spécialistes sectoriels dans le pétrole et le gaz, la logistique, l'ingénierie, la fabrication et les services portuaires.","u":"leadership.html"},{"id":"pg:leadership:6","t":"Direction","s":"Importateur pétrolier phare, exploitant de dépôts et réseau de détail  parmi les cinq premiers distributeurs de carburant de Tanzanie. DG : Abdulrahman Mohamed Une flotte logistique de plus de 700 camions pour le pétrole, le fret sec et le transport transfrontalier en Afrique de l'Est. Embouteillage de GPL, bouteilles composites et le plus grand terminal de stockage de GPL d'Afrique de l'Est, à Tanga.","u":"leadership.html"},{"id":"pg:leadership:7","t":"Direction","s":"Usine de formulation de lubrifiants à Dar es Salaam produisant des graisses et des huiles moteur pour les marchés régionaux. Fabrication d'acier, y compris les armatures HS-CR et les matériaux de construction pour les projets d'infrastructure. Gulf Concrete & Cement Products (GCCP) Béton prêt à l'emploi et granulats, leader du marché de l'approvisionnement en béton à Dar es Salaam.","u":"leadership.html"},{"id":"pg:leadership:8","t":"Direction","s":"Dépôt intérieur de conteneurs africain (AFICD) Services de dépôt ICD, CFS et de conteneurs vides avec logistique ferroviaire en Tanzanie. Développement de projets agricoles et de terrains vierges. Chef de projets : Nassoro Abubakari 21 nationalités. Une seule équipe. L'effectif de Lake Group reflète la riche diversité du continent africain, avec plus de 4 600 professionnels de 21 nationalités travaillant ensemble vers des objectifs communs.","u":"leadership.html"},{"id":"pg:leadership:9","t":"Direction","s":"© 2026 Lake Group. Tous droits réservés.","u":"leadership.html"},{"id":"pg:logistics:0","t":"Transport et acheminement","s":"Une flotte de plus de 700 camions assurant le transport de liquides en vrac et le transport régional de marchandises en Afrique de l'Est et centrale. L'épine dorsale de la chaîne d'approvisionnement d'Afrique de l'Est Lake Trans Ltd. est l'un des plus grands opérateurs logistiques d'Afrique de l'Est, exploitant une flotte de plus de 700 camions pour le transport de liquides en vrac, de marchandises générales et le transport régional transfrontalier.","u":"logistics.html"},{"id":"pg:logistics:1","t":"Transport et acheminement","s":"Des camions-citernes au fret sec, notre division transport assure une livraison rapide, sûre et économique vers des destinations en Tanzanie, au Kenya et en Zambie, et dans toute la région. ✓Transport de pétrole et de liquides en vrac ✓Fret sec et marchandises conteneurisées ✓Transport régional transfrontalier ✓Suivi de flotte en temps réel ✓Chauffeurs expérimentés et gestionnaires d'itinéraires","u":"logistics.html"},{"id":"pg:logistics:2","t":"Transport et acheminement","s":"Conçu pour les routes d'Afrique Camions-citernes spécialisés pour le transport sécurisé de liquides en vrac, entièrement conformes aux réglementations régionales sur les matières dangereuses. Camions plateaux et cargo robustes pour matériaux de construction, acier, conteneurs et fret général. Véhicules de transport GPL dédiés pour la livraison sécurisée de bouteilles et de gaz en vrac en Afrique de l'Est.","u":"logistics.html"},{"id":"pg:logistics:3","t":"Transport et acheminement","s":"© 2026 Lake Group. Tous droits réservés.","u":"logistics.html"},{"id":"pg:lpg:0","t":"Gaz GPL","s":"Alimenter les foyers, restaurants et industries de 7 pays d'Afrique de l'Est avec des bouteilles GPL sûres et fiables. Une énergie propre pour chaque cuisine Lake Gas Ltd. est l'entreprise de confiance d'embouteillage et de distribution de GPL en Afrique de l'Est, présente dans 6 pays. De la cuisine domestique aux grandes cuisines commerciales et aux applications industrielles, Lake Gas fournit un gaz de pétrole liquéfié sûr et fiable.","u":"lpg.html"},{"id":"pg:lpg:1","t":"Gaz GPL","s":"Notre gamme innovante de bouteilles composites, lancée à Dar es Salaam, marque une nouvelle révolution dans la technologie du gaz de cuisson, combinant sécurité et esthétique. Bouteille composite de 10 kg Nouveau © 2026 Lake Group. Tous droits réservés.","u":"lpg.html"},{"id":"pg:lubricants:0","t":"Lubrifiants","s":"Lubrifiants et produits lubrifiants Des lubrifiants automobiles, industriels et spécialisés de haute qualité, fabriqués et distribués en Afrique de l'Est et centrale. Lake Lubes Ltd., créée en 2014, fabrique et distribue une gamme complète de lubrifiants et de graisses pour les applications automobiles, industrielles et spécialisées en Afrique de l'Est et centrale.","u":"lubricants.html"},{"id":"pg:lubricants:1","t":"Lubrifiants","s":"Nos lubrifiants sont formulés pour répondre aux normes internationales, offrant une protection et des performances supérieures même dans les environnements d'exploitation les plus exigeants d'Afrique. Huiles moteur, fluides de transmission et graisses pour véhicules particuliers et utilitaires. Huiles industrielles robustes pour machines, compresseurs et équipements de fabrication.","u":"lubricants.html"},{"id":"pg:lubricants:2","t":"Lubrifiants","s":"Huiles pour engrenages, fluide de transmission automatique, liquides de refroidissement, huiles hydrauliques et graisses au lithium pour applications spécialisées. Analyse d'huile, conseils techniques et soutien à la maintenance pour les clients de flottes d'entreprise. © 2026 Lake Group. Tous droits réservés.","u":"lubricants.html"},{"id":"pg:media_center:0","t":"Actualités","s":"Communiqués de presse, déclarations officielles, vidéos d'entreprise et ressources médias téléchargeables pour Lake Group. Ally Edha Awadh nommé Jeune dirigeant d'entreprise de l'année Le fondateur et président du Groupe Lake, Ally Edha Awadh, a reçu le prix du Jeune dirigeant d'entreprise de l'année 2022 de l'African Leadership Magazine lors d'une cérémonie à la Chambre des Lords à Londres.","u":"media-center.html"},{"id":"pg:media_center:1","t":"Actualités","s":"Lake Gas porte le terminal GPL de Tanga à 3 000 tonnes Lake Gas a agrandi son terminal de Tanga  inauguré comme la plus grande installation de stockage de GPL d'Afrique de l'Est  de 1 000 à 3 000 tonnes, renforçant l'approvisionnement de la Tanzanie et des marchés voisins. Lake Gas lance les premières bouteilles de GPL composites d'Afrique","u":"media-center.html"},{"id":"pg:media_center:2","t":"Actualités","s":"Lake Gas a présenté les bouteilles de GPL composites  non explosives, anticorrosion, légères et translucides  lors d'un lancement à Dar es Salaam le 18 juin 2014, une première sur le marché africain. Pour les demandes d'interview, les questions de presse ou les partenariats médias, contactez notre équipe de communication. Lundi – vendredi, 9 h – 18 h (EAT)","u":"media-center.html"},{"id":"pg:media_center:3","t":"Actualités","s":"© 2026 Lake Group. Tous droits réservés.","u":"media-center.html"},{"id":"pg:news:0","t":"Actualités","s":"Les actualités du Groupe Lake  annonces, expansions, lancements de produits et activités communautaires. Lancement des bouteilles GPL composites Extension du terminal GPL de Tanga Pour les communiqués de presse, interviews ou partenariats médias : © 2026 Lake Group. Tous droits réservés.","u":"news.html"},{"id":"pg:projects:0","t":"Grands projets","s":"Une vitrine des projets de construction, d'infrastructure et d'approvisionnement majeurs réalisés par Lake Group en Afrique de l'Est. Au service du développement de l'Afrique de l'Est Des projets de construction de plusieurs millions de dollars aux contrats logistiques longue distance, Lake Group dispose de l'envergure, de l'expertise et des équipements nécessaires.","u":"projects.html"},{"id":"pg:projects:1","t":"Grands projets","s":"Terminal d'importation de GPL de Tanga  le plus grand d'Afrique de l'Est Lake Gas a construit à Tanga le plus grand terminal de stockage de GPL d'Afrique de l'Est  mis en service à 1 000 tonnes puis porté à 3 000 tonnes  doté d'une bouée d'amarrage dédiée permettant aux navires de décharger directement vers le terminal. Chaîne d'approvisionnement pétrolier panafricaine","u":"projects.html"},{"id":"pg:projects:2","t":"Grands projets","s":"Lake Oil et Lake Trans exploitent conjointement l'une des plus grandes chaînes d'approvisionnement en pétrole d'Afrique de l'Est, distribuant du carburant à 8 pays avec plus de 700 camions fonctionnant 24h/24. Laminoir Lake Steel, première en Tanzanie Premier producteur tanzanien de barres d'armature HS-CR. Le laminoir entièrement informatisé de Visiga, Kibaha, tourne jusqu'à 25 tonnes par heure  soit 100 000 tonnes de capacité annuelle  et ses barres sont approuvées pour les projets gouvernementaux.","u":"projects.html"},{"id":"pg:projects:3","t":"Grands projets","s":"MERM Ready Mix, expansion à Dubaï Middle East Ready Mix LLC (MERM), l'activité de béton prêt à l'emploi du Groupe Lake basée à Dubaï, produit du béton depuis 2005 et dessert de grands projets de construction dans tout Dubaï. Réseau de dépôts intérieurs de conteneurs africains AFICD exploite des dépôts de conteneurs intérieurs stratégiques en Tanzanie, en Zambie et au Mozambique, étendant la capacité portuaire vers l'arrière-pays et facilitant le commerce transfrontalier.","u":"projects.html"},{"id":"pg:projects:4","t":"Grands projets","s":"Lancement de la bouteille GPL composite Lake Gas a été pionnier dans l'introduction de bouteilles GPL composites en Afrique de l'Est, non explosives, légères et translucides, révolutionnant la sécurité du gaz de cuisson domestique. Vous avez un projet majeur nécessitant un soutien en énergie, logistique ou approvisionnement en construction ?","u":"projects.html"},{"id":"pg:projects:5","t":"Grands projets","s":"© 2026 Lake Group. Tous droits réservés.","u":"projects.html"},{"id":"pg:services:0","t":"Services ▾","s":"Des stations-service aux aciéries : huit secteurs, une seule vision, dans huit pays. Lake Group est présent sur toute la chaîne de valeur énergétique et industrielle de l'Afrique de l'Est et centrale. Top 5 des distributeurs de pétrole en Tanzanie. Plus de 85 stations-service, approvisionnement et stockage de pétrole en vrac. Embouteillage et distribution de GPL Lake Gas. Bouteilles de 6 kg, 10 kg, 15 kg et 38 kg à usage domestique et commercial dans 6 pays.","u":"services.html"},{"id":"pg:services:1","t":"Services ▾","s":"Lake Trans exploite plus de 700 camions pour le transport de liquides en vrac et de marchandises générales en Afrique de l'Est et centrale. GCCP, le principal fournisseur de béton prêt à l'emploi de Dar es Salaam. 30 000 m³ de granulats par mois. Lake Lubes fabrique et distribue des lubrifiants automobiles, industriels et spécialisés dans 5 pays.","u":"services.html"},{"id":"pg:services:2","t":"Services ▾","s":"Premier producteur de barres d'armature HS-CR en Tanzanie. Capacité du laminoir de 100 000 t/an. Services de dépôt de conteneurs intérieur et de gare de fret AFICD et ACFS en Tanzanie, en Zambie et au Mozambique. Opérations dans 8 pays plus Dubaï. Carte interactive de toutes les installations de Lake Group. Parlez à notre équipe de l'approvisionnement en carburant, de la logistique ou de l'un de nos services en Afrique de l'Est.","u":"services.html"},{"id":"pg:services:3","t":"Services ▾","s":"© 2026 Lake Group. Tous droits réservés.","u":"services.html"},{"id":"pg:station_locator:0","t":"Localisateur de stations","s":"Trouvez la station-service Lake Oil la plus proche et découvrez les services disponibles  les stations Lake Oil sont ouvertes 24h/24. Plus de 85 stations en Tanzanie Trouvez votre station Lake Oil la plus proche par ville ou région. Rechercher par ville ou région Les services en station comprennent Zone industrielle légère de Mikocheni, Dar es Salaam","u":"station-locator.html"},{"id":"pg:station_locator:1","t":"Localisateur de stations","s":"Ouvert 24h/24 | Essence, diesel, GPL Ouvert 24h/24 | Essence, diesel, lubrifiants Ville de Mwanza, région du lac Victoria Ouvert 24h/24 | Essence, diesel, diesel poids lourds Centre-ville de Dodoma, Dodoma © 2026 Lake Group. Tous droits réservés. ex. Dar es Salaam, Arusha, Mwanza...","u":"station-locator.html"},{"id":"pg:steel:0","t":"Lake Steel","s":"Premier producteur tanzanien de barres d'armature HS-CR. Laminoir entièrement informatisé d'une capacité annuelle de 100 000 tonnes. Premier en Tanzanie. Conçu pour durer. Lake Steel Ltd. est la première entreprise en Tanzanie à introduire des barres d'armature uniques à haute résistance et résistantes à la corrosion (HS-CR), un changement radical pour l'industrie de la construction en Afrique de l'Est.","u":"steel.html"},{"id":"pg:steel:1","t":"Lake Steel","s":"première entreprise en Tanzanie Notre laminoir d'acier de pointe, entièrement informatisé et automatique, a une capacité de production allant jusqu'à 25 tonnes par heure, soit une capacité annuelle de 100 000 tonnes métriques de barres d'acier de haute qualité. Nos barres HS-CR conservent leur résistance jusqu'à 600 °C, contre 350 °C pour les barres ordinaires, offrant des avantages essentiels en matière de résistance au feu pour les grands projets de construction.","u":"steel.html"},{"id":"pg:steel:2","t":"Lake Steel","s":"Zones de pollution industrielle Billettes testées dans notre laboratoire. Seuls les matériaux approuvés sont retenus. Billettes chauffées à la température de laminage dans notre four. Laminage informatisé d'une capacité de 25 t/h. Assurance qualité et expédition Tests de qualité selon les normes nationales et internationales avant expédition. © 2026 Lake Group. Tous droits réservés.","u":"steel.html"},{"id":"pg:sustainability:0","t":"RSE et durabilité","s":"L'engagement de Lake Group envers la responsabilité environnementale, la transition vers une énergie propre et la réduction de notre empreinte opérationnelle. De l'énergie pour l'Afrique. En toute responsabilité. En tant que grande entreprise d'énergie et de logistique présente dans 8 pays, Lake Group reconnaît sa responsabilité d'agir de manière à minimiser son impact environnemental et à contribuer au développement durable en Afrique.","u":"sustainability.html"},{"id":"pg:sustainability:1","t":"RSE et durabilité","s":"Notre stratégie de durabilité couvre la gérance environnementale, l'accès à une énergie de cuisson propre, la réhabilitation des terres, la gestion des déchets et la décarbonisation progressive de notre flotte logistique. Le GPL, activité principale de Lake Gas, joue un rôle essentiel dans l'agenda de cuisson propre en Afrique de l'Est, réduisant la dépendance au charbon de bois et au bois de chauffage, améliorant la qualité de l'air intérieur et réduisant la déforestation.","u":"sustainability.html"},{"id":"pg:sustainability:2","t":"RSE et durabilité","s":"Transition vers une cuisson propre Lake Gas fournit du GPL dans 6 pays, aidant les ménages à passer du charbon de bois à une cuisson plus propre. Chaque bouteille vendue réduit le CO₂, la pollution de l'air intérieur et la pression de déforestation. Les opérations de transport pétrolier visent zéro déversement. Les citernes sont régulièrement inspectées et entretenues dans les ateliers du Groupe à Kibaha, Kigamboni et Morogoro.","u":"sustainability.html"},{"id":"pg:sustainability:3","t":"RSE et durabilité","s":"Gestion responsable de la carrière La carrière de GCCP à Lugoba fournit les granulats des activités béton du Groupe. Nous nous engageons à une extraction responsable et à la réhabilitation progressive des zones exploitées. Investissement continu dans des camions plus récents et économes en carburant, réduisant les émissions par kilomètre de notre flotte de plus de 700 véhicules tout en améliorant la fiabilité du service.","u":"sustainability.html"},{"id":"pg:sustainability:4","t":"RSE et durabilité","s":"Pays ayant accès au GPL propre via Lake Gas Emplois locaux créés dans 8 pays Tolérance pour les incidents de déversement de pétrole m³ de granulats par mois, soutenant une construction durable © 2026 Lake Group. Tous droits réservés.","u":"sustainability.html"}]},"sw":{"docs":[{"id":"fact:countries","t":"Tunakofanya kazi","s":"Lake Group inafanya kazi katika nchi 8 za Afrika  Tanzania (makao makuu), Kenya, Zambia, DR Congo, Rwanda, Burundi, Ethiopia na Msumbiji  pamoja na uwepo katika Falme za Kiarabu (Dubai) kupitia MERM na SAFF.","u":"africa-network.html","k":"nchi gani wapi mnafanya kazi shughuli uwepo afrika mataifa mnaofanya","f":1},{"id":"fact:founding","t":"Kuanzishwa kwetu","s":"Lake Group ilianzishwa mwaka 2006 jijini Dar es Salaam, Tanzania, na Ally Edha Awadh, ikiwa na Lake Oil kama kampuni yake kuu. Imekua kuwa mojawapo ya makampuni ya biashara ya nishati na usafirishaji yanayokua kwa kasi zaidi Afrika Mashariki na Kati.","u":"about.html","k":"ilianzishwa lini historia mwaka mwanzilishi nani alianzisha","f":1},{"id":"fact:leadership","t":"Uongozi","s":"Ally Edha Awadh ni mwanzilishi, Mkurugenzi Mtendaji (CEO) na Mwenyekiti wa Lake Group. Alianzisha kampuni hii mwaka 2006 akiwa na miaka 27, kwa kituo kimoja tu cha mafuta Dar es Salaam.","u":"leadership.html","k":"mkurugenzi mtendaji mwenyekiti mwanzilishi uongozi nani anaongoza awadh kiongozi","f":1},{"id":"fact:contact","t":"Wasiliana nasi","s":"Makao makuu yetu: Plot 49, Mikocheni Light Industrial Area, S.L.P. 5055, Dar es Salaam, Tanzania. Simu: (+255) 222 780 510 au (+255) 222 780 479. Barua pepe: admin@lakeoilgroup.com.","u":"contact.html","k":"wasiliana mawasiliano simu barua pepe anwani makao makuu ofisi piga","f":1},{"id":"fact:workforce","t":"Watu wetu","s":"Lake Group inaajiri zaidi ya watu 4,600 wa mataifa 21 katika shughuli zake zote.","u":"about.html","k":"wafanyakazi waajiriwa wangapi idadi timu ajira watu","f":1},{"id":"fact:fleet","t":"Meli yetu ya magari","s":"Lake Trans, tawi la usafirishaji la kampuni lililoanzishwa mwaka 2008, linaendesha zaidi ya malori 700  kila lori likifuatiliwa kwa GPS  yakisafirisha mafuta na mizigo kwenda Zambia, Rwanda, DR Congo, Burundi, Malawi, Kenya na Uganda, yakiwa na karakana Kibaha, Kigamboni, Morogoro, Nairobi na Ndola.","u":"fleet.html","k":"malori magari mangapi usafirishaji lake trans karakana matenki","f":1},{"id":"fact:stations","t":"Vituo vya mafuta","s":"Lake Group inaendesha mitandao ya vituo vya mafuta kanda hii: vituo 85 Tanzania, 40 Kenya, 25 Zambia, 16 Burundi, 10 Rwanda na 8 DR Congo. Tumia ukurasa wa Kitafuta Vituo kupata kituo kilicho karibu nawe.","u":"station-locator.html","k":"vituo mafuta vingapi wapi kituo karibu petroli","f":1},{"id":"fact:lakeoil","t":"Lake Oil  mafuta na petroli","s":"Lake Oil, kampuni kuu ya kundi hili, ni miongoni mwa wasambazaji 5 bora wa bidhaa za petroli Tanzania. Ghala lake la Kigamboni, Dar es Salaam, lina uwezo wa kuhifadhi lita milioni 38 na bomba la moja kwa moja kutoka gati la kupokelea mafuta, likisaidiwa na vituo 85 vya rejareja na matenki 300 ya usafirishaji.","u":"fuel.html","k":"lake oil mafuta petroli dizeli ghala hifadhi kigamboni msambazaji","f":1},{"id":"fact:lakegas","t":"Lake Gas  gesi ya LPG","s":"Lake Gas inasambaza gesi ya LPG kwa rejareja na kwa wingi Tanzania, Zambia, DR Congo, Kenya, Burundi na Rwanda, kwa mitungi ya kilo 6, kilo 10 (composite), kilo 15 na kilo 38. Ilikuwa ya kwanza kuleta mitungi ya composite Afrika, na kituo chake cha Tanga kilijengwa kuwa ghala kubwa zaidi la kuhifadhi LPG Afrika Mashariki.","u":"lpg.html","k":"gesi lpg mitungi lake gas kupikia tanga mtungi","f":1},{"id":"fact:lakesteel","t":"Lake Steel","s":"Lake Steel ni kampuni ya kwanza Tanzania kuleta nondo imara zisizoshika kutu (HS-CR). Kiwanda chake cha kisasa kilichopo Kibaha kinazalisha hadi tani 25 kwa saa  takriban tani 100,000 kwa mwaka.","u":"steel.html","k":"chuma nondo hs-cr lake steel kiwanda vyuma","f":1},{"id":"fact:concrete","t":"GCCP  zege na kokoto","s":"GCCP (Gulf Concrete & Cement Products), iliyoanzishwa mwaka 2010, ndiyo msambazaji mkuu wa zege tayari (ready-mix) Dar es Salaam, ikiwa na mitambo ya kisasa ya kuchanganyia, machimbo yake ya Lugoba, pampu za kunyanyulia na malori 20 ya kuchanganyia zege ya mita za ujazo 12 kila moja. Gulf Aggregates inaendesha mitambo ya kusaga kokoto.","u":"concrete.html","k":"zege gccp saruji kokoto machimbo gulf simiti","f":1},{"id":"fact:lubricants","t":"Lake Lubes  mafuta ya kulainisha","s":"Lake Lubes, iliyoandikishwa Dar es Salaam mwaka 2014, inatengeneza na kusambaza mafuta ya kulainisha na grisi  ikiwemo LAKE 4T, LAKE HD SUPREME, LAKE POWER, mafuta ya gia, ATF, vipoza-injini na grisi  yanayouzwa kupitia mtandao wa vituo vya Lake Oil na nchi zote za kundi, pamoja na huduma ya kiufundi saa 24.","u":"lubricants.html","k":"mafuta ya kulainisha grisi lake lubes injini oili","f":1},{"id":"fact:containers","t":"Huduma za makontena","s":"AFICD (African Inland Container Depot) inatoa huduma za ICD, CFS na makontena matupu pale Tazara, Barabara ya Pugu, Dar es Salaam  yadi ya mita za mraba 14,000 yenye uwezo wa TEU 4,000 na reli inayounganisha bandarini  ikihudumia Rwanda, Burundi, Uganda, DR Congo, Zambia na Malawi. ACFS inaongeza kituo cha mizigo cha TEU 5,000.","u":"container-services.html","k":"makontena kontena icd cfs aficd acfs bandari mizigo","f":1},{"id":"fact:subsidiaries","t":"Kampuni za kundi","s":"Kampuni kuu za Lake Group ni Lake Oil (mafuta na petroli), Lake Gas (gesi ya LPG), Lake Trans (usafirishaji), Lake Lubes (mafuta ya kulainisha), Lake Steel (nondo za HS-CR), GCCP na Gulf Aggregates (zege na kokoto), AFICD na ACFS (huduma za makontena), pamoja na MERM (zege tayari) na SAFF (uwakala wa mizigo) huko Dubai.","u":"services.html","k":"kampuni tanzu matawi kundi biashara sekta mnafanya nini huduma","f":1},{"id":"fact:careers","t":"Ajira","s":"Daima tunatafuta watu wenye vipaji katika kampuni za kundi letu katika nchi 8. Tembelea ukurasa wa Ajira kuona nafasi zilizopo na kutuma maombi.","u":"careers.html","k":"ajira kazi nafasi kuajiriwa fursa maombi","f":1},{"id":"fact:values","t":"Maadili na utamaduni","s":"Maadili ya msingi ya Lake Group ni Ushirikiano, Kuaminika, Uadilifu na Kuridhika kwa Wateja, yakichagizwa na utamaduni wa Ubora, Huduma, Usalama na Weledi.","u":"about.html","k":"maadili utamaduni dhamira maono kanuni ubora usalama","f":1},{"id":"pg:hero:0","t":"Nyumbani","s":"Ilianzishwa 2006 · Dar es Salaam, Tanzania Tunaipa Nguvu Afrika Mashariki na ya Kati Mojawapo ya makampuni ya nishati, usafirishaji na ujenzi yanayokua kwa kasi zaidi barani Afrika, likifanya kazi katika nchi 8 likiwa na wafanyakazi 4,600+ na malori 700+ barabarani.","u":"index.html"},{"id":"pg:ose:0","t":"Kuhusu Sisi","s":"Akiwa na umri wa miaka 27, Ally Edha Awadh alifungua kituo kimoja cha mafuta jijini Dar es Salaam. Hakuwa na msafara wa magari, wala mtandao, wala uhakika. Ila imani tu kwamba Afrika Mashariki inastahili mnyororo wa ugavi wa nishati unaotegemewa zaidi. Ally Edha Awadh, Mwanzilishi & Mwenyekiti Lake Trans: usafirishaji wa mizigo kwa wingi Afrika Mashariki","u":"our-story.html"},{"id":"pg:ose:1","t":"Kuhusu Sisi","s":"tuliileta nishati safi nyumbani. Lake Gas sasa inasambaza mitungi ya LPG katika nchi sita, ikiondoa majiko ya mkaa na kuzipa familia njia salama zaidi ya kupika. Tulijenga zaidi ya kampuni ya mafuta. GCCP: msambazaji kiongozi wa zege tayari jijini Dar es Salaam Kila ghala, kila lori, kila mtungi unaendeshwa na watu. Watu 4,600+, kutoka mataifa 21, katika nchi 8. Hiyo ndiyo sehemu ambayo hakuna jedwali linaloweza kuinasa.","u":"our-story.html"},{"id":"pg:ose:2","t":"Kuhusu Sisi","s":"Tanzania &middot; Kenya &middot; Zambia &middot; Rwanda &middot; Burundi &middot; DRC &middot; Ethiopia &middot; Msumbiji Ubora. Huduma. Usalama. Weledi. Tukiipa nguvu Afrika Mashariki & ya Kati tangu 2006. \"Kutoka kituo kimoja cha mafuta hadi mojawapo ya makampuni makubwa zaidi ya nishati na viwanda Afrika Mashariki.\"","u":"our-story.html"},{"id":"pg:about:0","t":"Kuhusu Sisi","s":"Mojawapo ya makampuni ya biashara ya nishati na usafirishaji yanayokua kwa kasi zaidi Afrika Mashariki na Kati, lililoanzishwa 2006. Kutoka Kampuni Moja ya Mafuta hadi Nguzo ya Kikanda Lake Group ilianzishwa na Mkurugenzi Mtendaji na Mwenyekiti wake mwanzilishi Bw. Ally Edha Awadh mwaka 2006 kwa kufunguliwa kwa kampuni yake kuu, Lake Oil: mwanzo mnyenyekevu jijini Dar es Salaam, Tanzania.","u":"about.html"},{"id":"pg:about:1","t":"Kuhusu Sisi","s":"Tangu kuanzishwa kwake, ukuaji wa Lake Group umekuwa wa kasi ya juu, na kuwa mojawapo ya makampuni yanayokua kwa kasi zaidi katika biashara ya nishati, usafirishaji na vifaa vya ujenzi Afrika Mashariki na Kati pamoja na Mashariki ya Kati. Leo, Lake Group inasambaza bidhaa za petroli katika nchi 8, inamiliki maghala ya kuhifadhia kote kanda, inatengeneza vilainishi na zege tayari, na inaendesha msafara wa zaidi ya malori 700.","u":"about.html"},{"id":"pg:about:2","t":"Kuhusu Sisi","s":"Ikiwa na mchanganyiko wa mataifa 21 na jumla ya wafanyakazi 4,600+, Lake Group inaendelea kukua kwa dhamira. Kuwapatia wateja bidhaa na huduma bora kwa njia salama, yenye ufanisi na gharama nafuu bila kuharibu mazingira, tukitambua na kuingia katika maeneo mapya ya biashara huku tukijenga mazingira ya kazi ambapo wafanyakazi wanavuka viwango vyao binafsi vya ubora.","u":"about.html"},{"id":"pg:about:3","t":"Kuhusu Sisi","s":"Tukiongozwa na maadili yetu ya msingi: Ushirikiano, Kuaminika, Uadilifu na Kuridhika kwa Wateja. Ushirikiano, Kuaminika, Uadilifu Kuwa muuzaji rejareja na msambazaji kiongozi wa kikanda wa bidhaa na huduma huku tukifanikisha uboreshaji endelevu kupitia ubora wa uendeshaji, ubunifu na utamaduni unaozingatia utendaji. Tumejitolea kwa ubora wa hali ya juu","u":"about.html"},{"id":"pg:about:4","t":"Kuhusu Sisi","s":"Mkurugenzi Mtendaji na Mwenyekiti Alianzisha Lake Group akiwa na miaka 27 mwaka 2006 Neno kutoka kwa Mwanzilishi Wetu \"Karibu katika kampuni ya kipekee yenye shughuli mbalimbali: uuzaji wa mafuta, ubebaji wa mizigo, ujazaji wa gesi ya LPG, utengenezaji wa mitungi na uzalishaji wa zege. Tukiwa na timu yenye uzoefu katika vitengo vyote vya biashara, tuko tayari kikamilifu kukidhi mahitaji ya soko la kimataifa.\"","u":"about.html"},{"id":"pg:about:5","t":"Kuhusu Sisi","s":"Chini ya uongozi wa Bw. Awadh, Lake Group imejiimarisha kwa mafanikio katika Mafuta na Gesi, Uhandisi, Vifaa vya Viwandani, Miradi, Mizigo, Usambazaji, Biashara ya Jumla, Uhifadhi, Suluhisho za Zege na Sekta ya Ujenzi, ikijenga taasisi yenye kiwango cha juu cha kuaminika kimikopo kwa takriban miongo miwili. © 2026 Lake Group. Haki zote zimehifadhiwa.","u":"about.html"},{"id":"pg:africa_network:0","t":"Ramani ya Shughuli Afrika","s":"Ramani shirikishi ya uwepo wa Lake Group katika nchi 8 za Afrika Mashariki na Kati, pamoja na Dubai. Vituo vya Mafuta 85+, Buluu, Nyeupe, Njano na Nyekundu Malori 700+ · Wafanyakazi 4,600+ Tumeenea Kila Kona ya Afrika Mashariki na Kati Lake Group imeenea kijiografia katika kila kanda ya Tanzania na nchi jirani za Zambia, DRC, Burundi, Rwanda na Kenya, ikiwa na shughuli Ethiopia, Msumbiji na kiwanda kikubwa cha zege (premix) jijini Dubai.","u":"africa-network.html"},{"id":"pg:africa_network:1","t":"Ramani ya Shughuli Afrika","s":"Vituo vyetu vya mafuta vinatambulika papo hapo kwa rangi za kuvutia za buluu, nyeupe, njano na nyekundu, rangi zilezile maridadi za Lake Group utakazoziona kwenye ramani hapa chini. rangi za kuvutia za buluu, nyeupe, njano na nyekundu Makao Makuu · kampuni tanzu 10 Lake Oil Ltd.: Usambazaji wa Petroli Lake Trans Ltd.: Usafiri na Ubebaji wa Mizigo","u":"africa-network.html"},{"id":"pg:africa_network:2","t":"Ramani ya Shughuli Afrika","s":"Lake Gas Ltd.: Ujazaji na Usambazaji wa LPG Lake Lubes Ltd.: Utengenezaji wa Vilainishi Lake Steel Ltd.: Kiwanda cha Nondo za HS-CR GCCP Co. Ltd.: Zege Tayari (Ready-Mix) AFICD: Bandari Kavu ya Makontena ya Afrika ACFS: Kituo cha Mizigo ya Makontena SAFF: Uwakala wa Mizigo na Usafirishaji Gulf Aggregate: Usagaji wa Mawe Lake Gas Ltd.: Usambazaji wa LPG","u":"africa-network.html"},{"id":"pg:africa_network:3","t":"Ramani ya Shughuli Afrika","s":"AFICD: Bandari Kavu ya Makontena MERM: Middle East Ready Mix LLC Mojawapo ya shughuli kubwa zaidi za zege iliyochanganywa tayari za Kundi la Lake, ikihudumia miradi mikubwa ya ujenzi Dubai. Mipaka ya nchi imeonyeshwa kwa nyeupe · Nchi za Lake Group kwa dhahabu · Nukta za rangi = miundombinu Kwa Nini Lake Group Inajipambanua Kote Afrika Misingi ileile inayoendesha ukurasa wetu wa mwanzo, ubora, huduma, usalama na weledi, inaongoza kila soko tunalofanyia kazi.","u":"africa-network.html"},{"id":"pg:africa_network:4","t":"Ramani ya Shughuli Afrika","s":"Ubora haujadiliwi, kuanzia mafuta na LPG hadi chuma, vilainishi na zege tayari. Viwango vya juu kabisa vya huduma na ugavi thabiti wa mafuta pamoja na huduma kwa wateja katika kila eneo. Usalama ni wa kwanza katika yote tunayofanya, kwenye maghala, misafara ya malori, vituo vya LPG na maeneo ya ujenzi. Weledi ndio utamaduni tunaouthamini, wafanyakazi 4,600+ kutoka mataifa 21, timu moja.","u":"africa-network.html"},{"id":"pg:africa_network:5","t":"Ramani ya Shughuli Afrika","s":"Maghala ya mafuta, vituo vya LPG, misafara ya malori, bandari kavu za makontena na viwanda vya zege, vyote vimeunganishwa kupitia mtandao wetu wa Afrika. © 2026 Lake Group. Haki zote zimehifadhiwa.","u":"africa-network.html"},{"id":"pg:careers:0","t":"Ajira","s":"Daima tunatafuta wataalamu wenye vipaji na ari ya kazi kujiunge na timu yetu inayokua kote Afrika Mashariki na Kati. Jenga Taaluma Yako Kote Afrika Lake Group inatoa ajira zenye matokeo ya kweli; utafanya kazi katika mojawapo ya biashara zinazokua kwa kasi zaidi Afrika Mashariki, ukiwa na fursa za kweli za kukua, kuongoza na kuleta mabadiliko.","u":"careers.html"},{"id":"pg:careers:1","t":"Ajira","s":"Tukiwa na wafanyakazi zaidi ya 4,600 katika nchi 8 na mataifa 21, sisi ni timu halisi ya Kiafrika inayounganishwa na maadili ya pamoja: Ubora, Huduma, Usalama na Weledi. Fursa za kupanda ngazi kati ya nchi na divisheni mbalimbali Fanya kazi kwenye miradi inayochagiza maendeleo ya Afrika Mashariki Fanya kazi bega kwa bega na watu wa mataifa 21 katika nchi 8","u":"careers.html"},{"id":"pg:careers:2","t":"Ajira","s":"Viwango vya usalama vinavyoongoza sekta katika shughuli zote Maghala, vituo na viwanda vya Kundi Viwanda vya chuma, zege na LPG Hata kama hakuna nafasi mahususi inayolingana na wasifu wako, tunakaribisha maombi ya jumla kutoka kwa wataalamu wenye vipaji. © 2026 Lake Group. Haki zote zimehifadhiwa. Tueleze kukuhusu na unachoweza kukileta Lake Group...","u":"careers.html"},{"id":"pg:concrete:0","t":"Zege na Kokoto","s":"Zege Tayari (Ready-Mix) na Kokoto Gulf Concrete and Cement Products, msambazaji anayeongoza soko la zege tayari jijini Dar es Salaam tangu mwaka 2010. Tunajenga Mustakabali wa Afrika Mashariki Gulf Concrete and Cement Products Company Ltd (GCCP), iliyoanzishwa mwaka 2010, ni miongoni mwa wasambazaji wakuu wa zege tayari jijini Dar es Salaam, ikishiriki katika miradi mingi ya ujenzi yenye hadhi kubwa zaidi jijini.","u":"concrete.html"},{"id":"pg:concrete:1","t":"Zege na Kokoto","s":"GCCP inamiliki machimbo yake yenyewe huko Lugoba yenye mitambo miwili ya kokoto yenye uwezo wa tani 250 kwa saa kila mmoja, ikizalisha m³ 30,000 za kokoto kwa mwezi. Shughuli zake za zege tayari zinaendeshwa na mitambo ya kuchanganyia ya Sany International kutoka China. Huko Dubai, Lake Group inaendesha MERM (Middle East Ready Mix LLC), mmoja wa mitambo mikubwa zaidi ya zege tayari katika ukanda huo.","u":"concrete.html"},{"id":"pg:concrete:2","t":"Zege na Kokoto","s":"MERM (Middle East Ready Mix LLC) Malori ya Kuchanganya Zege (12m³) ✓Mitambo ya kuchanganyia zege inayojiendesha kikamilifu ya Sany International ✓Mitambo 2 ya kusaga kokoto (250T/hr kila mmoja) ✓Pampu 4 za zege zisizohamishika (Sany International) ✓Pampu 2 za mkono mrefu (urefu wa mkono 32m) ✓Machimbo yetu wenyewe huko Lugoba, Tanzania Kwa miradi inayohitaji kuondoa fremu haraka na ratiba za ujenzi zilizoharakishwa.","u":"concrete.html"},{"id":"pg:concrete:3","t":"Zege na Kokoto","s":"Mchanganyiko wenye msinyao mdogo kwa ajili ya sakafu, njia za lami na miundo ambako udhibiti wa nyufa ni muhimu. Zege Inayojishindilia Yenyewe (SCC) Inatiririka na kujishindilia kwa uzito wake yenyewe; bora kwa maeneo yenye nondo nyingi zilizosongamana. Zege yenye umaliziaji wa hali ya juu kwa kuta za mbele za majengo, nyuso za mapambo na sehemu za muundo zinazoonekana.","u":"concrete.html"},{"id":"pg:concrete:4","t":"Zege na Kokoto","s":"Zege inayopitisha maji kwa mifereji endelevu ya maji kwenye maegesho ya magari, barabara na mandhari. Zege yenye nguvu ya juu na uimara mkubwa kwa nguzo za msingi, misingi ya kina na miundo muhimu. © 2026 Lake Group. Haki zote zimehifadhiwa.","u":"concrete.html"},{"id":"pg:contact:0","t":"Mawasiliano","s":"Wasiliana na timu yetu kwa maswali, ushirikiano, nukuu za bei au taarifa yoyote kuhusu Lake Group na kampuni zake tanzu. Tunafurahi Kusikia Kutoka Kwako Kiwanja Na. 49, Eneo la Viwanda Vyepesi la Mikocheni S.L.P 5055, Dar es Salaam, Tanzania Mikocheni, Dar es Salaam, Tanzania Kuratibu: -6.762806, 39.241447 © 2026 Lake Group. Haki zote zimehifadhiwa.","u":"contact.html"},{"id":"pg:container_services:0","t":"Huduma za Makontena","s":"African Inland Container Depot (AFICD) na Container Freight Station (ACFS), suluhisho za upanuzi wa bandari kote Afrika Mashariki. Lango la Ndani ya Nchi la Biashara ya Afrika Mashariki AFICD (African Inland Container Depot) na ACFS (African Container Freight Station) ni mikono ya Lake Group ya usafirishaji wa bandarini, ikitoa huduma muhimu za kuhifadhi makontena, kuyashughulikia na huduma za forodha zinazopanua uwezo wa bandari hadi maeneo ya bara.","u":"container-services.html"},{"id":"pg:container_services:1","t":"Huduma za Makontena","s":"Tukiwa na shughuli nchini Tanzania, Zambia na Msumbiji, huduma zetu za makontena zimewekwa kwenye korido za kimkakati ili kuhudumia waagizaji, wasafirishaji nje na kampuni za meli za kanda. ✓Kuhifadhi na kupanga makontena ✓Kupakia na kupakua mizigo kwenye makontena (LCL/FCL) ✓Ukaguzi wa forodha na msaada wa uondoshaji wa mizigo ✓Kushughulikia makontena ya majokofu (reefer)","u":"container-services.html"},{"id":"pg:container_services:2","t":"Huduma za Makontena","s":"✓Ukarabati na matengenezo ya makontena ✓Muunganiko na mtandao wa malori wa Lake Trans Dar es Salaam, lango la uchumi mkubwa zaidi Afrika Mashariki Bohari ya ndani ya nchi inayohudumia korido ya Zambia–Tanzania Usafirishaji wa bandari wa kimkakati kwa biashara ya korido ya Beira © 2026 Lake Group. Haki zote zimehifadhiwa.","u":"container-services.html"},{"id":"pg:csr:0","t":"CSR na Uendelevu","s":"Uwajibikaji kwa Jamii na Uendelevu Lake Group imejizatiti kurudisha kwa jamii inazozihudumia na kuendesha shughuli zake kwa athari ndogo kabisa kwa mazingira. Ukuaji Wenye Uwajibikaji. Matokeo ya Kudumu. Ikiwa mojawapo ya waajiri wakubwa zaidi wa sekta binafsi Afrika Mashariki, Lake Group inachukulia kwa uzito majukumu yake ya kijamii na kimazingira. Kundi hutoa mara kwa mara msaada kwa maendeleo ya jamii kupitia shughuli zake nyingi za uwajibikaji kwa jamii, na ni miongoni mwa vinara kati ya wenzake.","u":"csr.html"},{"id":"pg:csr:1","t":"CSR na Uendelevu","s":"Tunaamini kwamba ukuaji wa biashara na maendeleo ya jamii huenda pamoja, na kwamba mafanikio yetu lazima yalete manufaa ya dhahiri kwa watu na mazingira tunayofanyia kazi. Programu za uwajibikaji kwa jamii zinaendelea Mazoea ya uwajibikaji kwa mazingira Misaada ya afya, yatima na dharura Jinsi Tunavyorudisha kwa Jamii Kutoa vifaa tiba kwa wodi za wazazi katika hospitali za manispaa za Dar es Salaam  vitanda vya kujifungulia, vifaa vya kujifungulia, viti vya magurudumu, machela na mashine za kupima presha  na kusaidia hospitali za rufaa kama Temeke.","u":"csr.html"},{"id":"pg:csr:2","t":"CSR na Uendelevu","s":"Kusaidia watoto wenye uhitaji na vituo vya yatima, kuunga mkono nyumba za ibada, na kutoa msaada wa dharura  ikiwemo chakula na mitungi ya gesi ya kupikia kwa familia zilizoathiriwa na mafuriko Rufiji. Ushughulikiaji, uhifadhi na usafirishaji wa uwajibikaji wa bidhaa za petroli katika mnyororo mzima wa ugavi, pamoja na uwekezaji endelevu katika vifaa vya kisasa na shughuli safi zaidi.","u":"csr.html"},{"id":"pg:csr:3","t":"CSR na Uendelevu","s":"Ajira zaidi ya 4,600 katika nchi 8, tukiwa na kipaumbele kikubwa cha kuajiri na kukuza vipaji vya wenyeji katika kila ngazi ya taasisi. Upatikanaji wa Nishati Safi ya Kupikia Kupanua upatikanaji wa uhakika wa LPG kwa kaya Afrika Mashariki  kupunguza utegemezi wa mkaa, kuboresha hewa ndani ya nyumba na kupunguza shinikizo la ukataji miti. Viwango vya usalama vinavyoongoza sekta katika divisheni zote. Lengo la kutokuwa na madhara yoyote kwa wafanyakazi, wakandarasi na jamii tunazofanyia kazi.","u":"csr.html"},{"id":"pg:csr:4","t":"CSR na Uendelevu","s":"© 2026 Lake Group. Haki zote zimehifadhiwa.","u":"csr.html"},{"id":"pg:fleet:0","t":"Msafara Wetu","s":"Msafara wa Magari wa Lake Trans Malori zaidi ya 700 yaliyoundwa maalum yanayofanya kazi saa 24, siku 7 kote Afrika Mashariki na Kati  uti wa mgongo wa shughuli zetu za usafirishaji. Yaliyoundwa Maalum kwa Kila Mzigo Malori makubwa ya matangi kwa usafirishaji wa mafuta kwa wingi, yenye uwezo wa lita 12,000 hadi 40,000. Kila tanki linafuatiliwa kwa GPS na linaendeshwa kwa leseni kamili za kisheria.","u":"fleet.html"},{"id":"pg:fleet:1","t":"Msafara Wetu","s":"Trela za flatbed na zenye mapazia zinazofaa kwa chuma, vifaa vya ujenzi, makontena na mizigo mikubwa kupita kiasi kote kanda. Matenki maalum ya shinikizo kwa usafirishaji wa LPG kwa wingi kati ya viwanda vya kujaza mitungi na vituo vya usambazaji kote Afrika Mashariki. Usambazaji wa Jumla na Mitungi Malori 20 ya kuchanganya zege (12m³ kila moja) yaliyotengwa kwa uwasilishaji wa zege tayari wa GCCP kwenye maeneo ya ujenzi kote Dar es Salaam.","u":"fleet.html"},{"id":"pg:fleet:2","t":"Msafara Wetu","s":"Mitambo ya Kushughulikia Makontena Mitambo ya kunyanyua makontena (reach stackers), matrekta ya vituo na malori ya makontena kwa shughuli za bohari za ndani za AFICD nchini Tanzania, Zambia na Msumbiji. Kundi la magari ya msaada la pikapu, magari ya huduma na magari ya wasimamizi kwa shughuli za uwandani, matengenezo na msaada wa uwasilishaji wa hatua ya mwisho.","u":"fleet.html"},{"id":"pg:fleet:3","t":"Msafara Wetu","s":"© 2026 Lake Group. Haki zote zimehifadhiwa.","u":"fleet.html"},{"id":"pg:fuel:0","t":"Mafuta na Petroli","s":"Usambazaji wa Mafuta na Petroli Mojawapo ya wasambazaji 5 bora wa mafuta ya petroli Tanzania, ikisambaza mafuta bora katika nchi 8 za Afrika Mashariki na Kati. Tunaifanya Afrika Isonge Mbele Lake Oil Ltd. ni kampuni kinara ya Lake Group na mojawapo ya wasambazaji 5 bora wa bidhaa za petroli nchini Tanzania. Ilianzishwa mwaka 2006 na imejenga uwepo imara kote Afrika Mashariki na Kati.","u":"fuel.html"},{"id":"pg:fuel:1","t":"Mafuta na Petroli","s":"Tunasambaza bidhaa nyeupe za petroli  petroli na dizeli  kupitia vituo vya rejareja, usambazaji wa jumla na maghala ya kimkakati kote kanda, na kutoa huduma za kujaza mafuta meli zinazotia nanga katika bandari ya Dar es Salaam. ✓Vituo vya mafuta vya rejareja, zaidi ya 85 Tanzania na kanda nzima ✓Usambazaji wa mafuta kwa wingi kwa wateja wa kampuni na serikali","u":"fuel.html"},{"id":"pg:fuel:2","t":"Mafuta na Petroli","s":"✓Miundombinu yetu wenyewe ya kuhifadhi mafuta Tanzania, Kenya, Burundi na DRC ✓Bei shindani zinazoungwa mkono na ukubwa wa mnyororo wa ugavi wa kanda ✓Bidhaa bora zinazokidhi viwango vya kitaifa na kimataifa Imeorodheshwa miongoni mwa wasambazaji 5 bora wa mafuta ya petroli Tanzania kwa ujazo. Miundombinu ya kimkakati ya kuhifadhi Tanzania, Kenya, Burundi na DRC.","u":"fuel.html"},{"id":"pg:fuel:3","t":"Mafuta na Petroli","s":"Msafara wa magari uliounganishwa kwa uwasilishaji wa uhakika na kwa wakati kila mara. Uwezo wa kusambaza mafuta kote Afrika Mashariki na Kati. © 2026 Lake Group. Haki zote zimehifadhiwa.","u":"fuel.html"},{"id":"pg:gallery:0","t":"Matunzio","s":"Picha halisi kutoka kwenye shughuli zetu, kiwanda cha zege cha GCCP, MERM Dubai, mitungi ya gesi ya LPG, shughuli za mafuta na zaidi. Picha halisi zilizopatikana moja kwa moja kutoka lakeoilgroup.com, zikionyesha shughuli zetu Afrika Mashariki na Mashariki ya Kati. Shughuli za Uwandani kote Afrika Mashariki Viwango vya Juu Kabisa vya Huduma Wasambazaji Wakubwa Zaidi wa Mafuta ya Petroli Tanzania","u":"gallery.html"},{"id":"pg:gallery:1","t":"Matunzio","s":"Kampuni Inayokua kwa Kasi Zaidi Afrika Shughuli za Mnyororo wa Ugavi Afrika Nzima Mtandao wa Usambazaji wa Mafuta Ubora, Huduma, Usalama, Weledi Bidhaa za Petroli kote Afrika Mashariki Lake Oil Ltd.: Shughuli za Vituo vya Mafuta Lake Oil Ltd.: Shughuli za Ugavi wa Mafuta ya Petroli Lake Gas Ltd.: Usambazaji wa LPG kote Afrika Mashariki Lake Gas, Mtungi wa LPG wa 6kg kwa Matumizi ya Nyumbani","u":"gallery.html"},{"id":"pg:gallery:2","t":"Matunzio","s":"Lake Gas, Mtungi wa 15kg kwa Hoteli na Migahawa Lake Gas, Mtungi wa LPG wa Kibiashara wa 38kg Lake Gas, Mtungi wa Composite wa 10kg (Haulipuki, Angavu Lake Gas, Aina Mbalimbali za Mitungi ya Composite GCCP, Kiwanda cha Kuchanganyia Zege cha Gulf, Dar es Salaam GCCP, Kiwanda cha Kokoto cha Sany International (250T/hr) GCCP, Shughuli za Uwasilishaji wa Zege Tayari","u":"gallery.html"},{"id":"pg:gallery:3","t":"Matunzio","s":"GCCP, Msafara wa Malori ya Kuchanganyia Zege (magari 20, 12m³ kila moja) GCCP, Pampu ya Zege ya Boom (32m) kwenye Eneo la Ujenzi GCCP, Maabara ya Uhakiki wa Ubora na Upimaji GCCP, Muonekano wa Kiwanda, Eneo la Vijibweni GCCP, Mitambo Mizito na Mifumo ya Sany ya Kuchanganyia Zege GCCP, Ugavi wa Zege Tayari kwa Miradi ya Kifahari GCCP, Uzalishaji wa Kokoto katika Machimbo ya Lugoba","u":"gallery.html"},{"id":"pg:gallery:4","t":"Matunzio","s":"GCCP, Shughuli za Zege la Misingi na Nguzo GCCP, Upakiaji wa Lori la Kuchanganyia Zege Kiwandani MERM: Middle East Ready Mix LLC, Dubai, Falme za Kiarabu MERM: Mojawapo ya Mitambo Mikubwa ya Zege ya Kundi la Lake MERM: Msafara wa Zege Tayari, Dubai MERM: Shughuli za Kiwanda cha Kuchanganyia Zege, Dubai MERM: Ugavi wa Zege kwa Miradi ya Ujenzi Falme za Kiarabu","u":"gallery.html"},{"id":"pg:gallery:5","t":"Matunzio","s":"MERM: Msafara wa Malori ya Zege katika Kiwanda cha Dubai MERM: Hifadhi ya Kokoto na Malighafi, Falme za Kiarabu MERM: Maabara ya Udhibiti wa Ubora, Dubai MERM: Njia ya Uzalishaji wa Zege Tayari, Falme za Kiarabu MERM: Shughuli za Lake Group Mashariki ya Kati Picha 39 halisi kutoka kwenye shughuli za Lake Group, GCCP, MERM Dubai, Lake Gas, Lake Oil na zaidi.","u":"gallery.html"},{"id":"pg:gallery:6","t":"Matunzio","s":"© 2026 Lake Group. Haki zote zimehifadhiwa.","u":"gallery.html"},{"id":"pg:history:0","t":"Historia Yetu","s":"Kutoka kituo kimoja cha mafuta hadi kuwa kundi la makampuni linaloenea Afrika nzima, hii ni safari ya Lake Group tangu 2006. Simulizi ya maamuzi ya kijasiri, upanuzi usiokoma, na ujenzi wa himaya ya nishati kuanzia chini kabisa. Ally Edha Awadh anaanzisha Lake Oil Ltd. akiwa na umri wa miaka 27 jijini Dar es Salaam, Tanzania, mbegu ya kile ambacho kingekuja kuwa Lake Group. Anaanza usambazaji wa mafuta ya petroli kwa msafara mdogo wa magari.","u":"history.html"},{"id":"pg:history:1","t":"Historia Yetu","s":"Usafirishaji na Hatua za Kwanza za Kikanda Lake Trans Ltd. inaanzishwa kama tawi la usafirishaji la Kundi. Mwaka huo huo, DRC Petroleum S.A.R.L. inaanzishwa katika Jamhuri ya Kidemokrasia ya Kongo na Lake Petroleum Ltd. inasajiliwa nchini Zambia  hatua za kwanza za Kundi nje ya Tanzania. Kampuni ya Gulf Concrete and Cement Products (GCCP) inaanzishwa, na kwa haraka inakuwa kinara wa soko la ugavi wa zege tayari jijini Dar es Salaam.","u":"history.html"},{"id":"pg:history:2","t":"Historia Yetu","s":"Uwepo Afrika Mashariki Wapanuka Burundi Petroleum inafungua kituo chake cha kwanza cha mafuta nchini Burundi, na Lake Petroleum Rwanda  iliyoanzishwa Kigali mwaka 2011  inaanza kuagiza na kusambaza mafuta kote Rwanda. Vilainishi na Mitungi ya Komposi Lake Lubes Ltd. inaanzishwa Dar es Salaam kuchanganya na kuuza vilainishi vya Kundi, na Lake Gas inazindua mitungi ya kwanza ya LPG ya komposi barani Afrika  isiyolipuka, nyepesi na inayopitisha mwanga.","u":"history.html"},{"id":"pg:history:3","t":"Historia Yetu","s":"Kuingia Kenya kwa Kiwango Kikubwa Mamlaka ya Ushindani ya Kenya inaidhinisha Lake Oil kununua mtandao wa vituo vya mafuta vya Hashi Energy nchini Kenya  hatua muhimu katika soko kubwa zaidi la rejareja la mafuta Afrika Mashariki. Lake Gas inawekeza Tanga na kuanzisha kituo kilichofunguliwa kikiwa kikubwa zaidi cha kuhifadhi LPG Afrika Mashariki  uwezo wa tani 1,000, kikipokea meli kupitia boya maalum la kufungia meli.","u":"history.html"},{"id":"pg:history:4","t":"Historia Yetu","s":"Lake Steel and Allied Products inaanza shughuli zake Visiga, Kibaha  mzalishaji wa kwanza wa nondo imara zenye ukinzani wa kutu (HS-CR) nchini Tanzania, na uwezo wa tani 100,000 kwa mwaka. Kituo cha LPG cha Tanga kinapanuliwa hadi tani 3,000, na mwanzilishi Ally Edha Awadh anatunukiwa tuzo ya Kiongozi Kijana wa Biashara wa Mwaka na jarida la African Leadership.","u":"history.html"},{"id":"pg:history:5","t":"Historia Yetu","s":"Wafanyakazi 4,600+. Nchi 8. Bado Tunakua. Lake Group inaendelea kupanuka, ikiimarisha uwepo wake wa kikanda, ikiwekeza katika teknolojia mpya, na kuchochea maendeleo ya kiuchumi kote Afrika Mashariki na Kati. Kuwa Sehemu ya Sura Inayofuata Jiunge na timu yetu au shirikiana nasi kote Afrika. © 2026 Lake Group. Haki zote zimehifadhiwa.","u":"history.html"},{"id":"pg:index:0","t":"Nyumbani","s":"Usambazaji wa Mafuta ya Petroli Ujazaji na Usambazaji wa Gesi ya LPG Usafirishaji wa Vimiminika kwa Wingi Utengenezaji wa Mafuta ya Kulainisha Kutoka makao makuu yetu Dar es Salaam, Lake Group inaendesha shughuli katika nchi nane  Tanzania, Kenya, Zambia, Rwanda, Burundi, DR Congo, Ethiopia na Msumbiji  pamoja na kituo cha Dubai kinachounganisha mtandao huo na masoko ya kimataifa.","u":"index.html"},{"id":"pg:index:1","t":"Nyumbani","s":"Mtazamo wa KimataifaMwonekano mmoja wa mtandao unaosafirisha nishati Afrika Mashariki na Kati. Uwepo WetuNchi nane zinahudumiwa kutoka Dar es Salaam kwa msafara wa malori 700+. UwandaniVituo 85+ vya mafuta Tanzania, ghala la LPG la Tanga na huduma za kujaza mafuta meli katika bandari ya Dar es Salaam. Kundi la Makampuni Lililojengwa kwa Ukakamavu na Maono","u":"index.html"},{"id":"pg:index:2","t":"Nyumbani","s":"Ikianzishwa na Mkurugenzi Mtendaji Mkuu na Mwenyekiti Ally Edha Awadh mwaka 2006 akiwa na umri wa miaka 27 tu, Lake Group imekua kutoka kituo kimoja cha mafuta hadi kuwa mojawapo ya makundi makubwa zaidi ya nishati, usafirishaji na viwanda Afrika Mashariki na Kati. Leo, ikiwa na wafanyakazi 4,600+ kutoka mataifa 21, malori 700+, vituo vya mafuta 85+ na kampuni tanzu 20+, Lake Group inawezesha maisha ya kila siku kote Tanzania, Kenya, Zambia, Rwanda, Burundi, DRC, Ethiopia na Msumbiji.","u":"index.html"},{"id":"pg:index:3","t":"Nyumbani","s":"Kutoka vituo vya mafuta hadi viwanda vya chuma, Lake Group inafanya kazi katika mnyororo mzima wa thamani wa nishati na viwanda wa Afrika Mashariki. Miongoni mwa wasambazaji 5 bora wa mafuta ya petroli Tanzania. Vituo vya rejareja, ugavi kwa wingi na uhifadhi katika nchi 8. Lake Gas inaendesha ujazaji na usambazaji wa gesi ya LPG kwa mitungi ya matumizi ya nyumbani na ya kibiashara katika nchi 6.","u":"index.html"},{"id":"pg:index:4","t":"Nyumbani","s":"Usafirishaji na Ubebaji Mizigo Lake Trans inaendesha malori 700+ kwa usafirishaji wa vimiminika kwa wingi na usafirishaji wa kikanda kote Afrika Mashariki na Kati. GCCP, msambazaji mkuu wa zege tayari jijini Dar es Salaam. Kokoto 30,000 m³ kila mwezi kutoka machimbo yetu ya Lugoba. Lake Lubes hutengeneza na kusambaza vilainishi bora vya magari, viwanda na matumizi maalum katika nchi 5.","u":"index.html"},{"id":"pg:index:5","t":"Nyumbani","s":"Mzalishaji wa kwanza wa nondo za HS-CR Tanzania. Kiwanda cha kusindika chuma kinachojiendesha kikamilifu, chenye uwezo wa 100,000 MT kwa mwaka. AFICD na ACFS zinatoa huduma za depo za makontena za bara na vituo vya mizigo kote TZ, ZM na MZ. Shughuli kote Tanzania, Kenya, Zambia, Rwanda, Burundi, DRC, Ethiopia, Msumbiji na Dubai. Ujumbe kutoka kwa Mkurugenzi Mtendaji Mkuu","u":"index.html"},{"id":"pg:index:6","t":"Nyumbani","s":"Neno kutoka kwa Mwanzilishi Wetu \"Karibu kwenye kampuni ya kipekee iliyo mstari wa mbele katika uuzaji wa mafuta, usafirishaji, ujazaji wa gesi ya LPG, utengenezaji wa mitungi na uzalishaji wa zege. Tukiwa na wahandisi wenye uzoefu na wataalamu wa biashara katika vitengo vyetu vyote, tuko tayari kikamilifu kukidhi mahitaji ya soko la dunia.\"","u":"index.html"},{"id":"pg:index:7","t":"Nyumbani","s":"Mkurugenzi Mtendaji Mkuu na Mwenyekiti, Lake Group | Alianzisha Lake Group akiwa na miaka 27 mwaka 2006 Uko Tayari Kufanya Kazi Pamoja Nasi? Zungumza na timu yetu kuhusu ugavi wa mafuta, usafirishaji, au huduma zetu nyingine zozote kote Afrika Mashariki. © 2026 Lake Group. Haki zote zimehifadhiwa.","u":"index.html"},{"id":"pg:investors:0","t":"Mahusiano ya Wawekezaji","s":"Vivutio vya kifedha, wasifu wa ukuaji wa kampuni na taarifa za utawala bora kwa wawekezaji wa sasa na watarajiwa. Rekodi Iliyothibitika ya Ukuaji wa Wima Lake Group imeonyesha ukuaji thabiti na mkubwa tangu kuanzishwa kwake mwaka 2006. Kutoka msambazaji mmoja wa mafuta ya petroli jijini Dar es Salaam, imekua na kuwa kundi la makampuni ya sekta mbalimbali linalofanya kazi katika nchi 8 likiwa na kampuni tanzu zaidi ya 20.","u":"investors.html"},{"id":"pg:investors:1","t":"Mahusiano ya Wawekezaji","s":"Nguvu yetu ya kifedha, kiwango cha juu cha uaminifu wa mikopo katika jumuiya ya biashara ya kimataifa, na vyanzo mbalimbali vya mapato katika nishati, usafirishaji na vifaa vya ujenzi vinaifanya Lake Group kuwa uwekezaji imara na wenye fursa kubwa. Kundi hili linamilikiwa kibinafsi, lina makao makuu Tanzania, na lina athari ya moja kwa moja ya kiuchumi katika kila soko linalofanya kazi, likisaidia ajira za ndani, minyororo ya ugavi na maendeleo ya miundombinu.","u":"investors.html"},{"id":"pg:investors:2","t":"Mahusiano ya Wawekezaji","s":"Njia nane tofauti za biashara katika nishati, usafirishaji, utengenezaji na ujenzi zinapunguza hatari ya kutegemea sekta moja na kutoa mapato thabiti ya vyanzo vingi. Shughuli katika masoko 8 ya Afrika Mashariki na Kati yanayokua kwa kasi, baadhi yakiwa ni uchumi unaokua kwa kasi zaidi duniani kwa Pato la Taifa na idadi ya watu. Kutoka kampuni 1 mwaka 2006 hadi kampuni tanzu zaidi ya 20  rekodi ya upanuzi wenye nidhamu na uundaji wa thamani kwa karibu miongo miwili.","u":"investors.html"},{"id":"pg:investors:3","t":"Mahusiano ya Wawekezaji","s":"Tunamiliki maghala ya kuhifadhia, msafara wa malori (700+), kiwanda cha kusindika chuma, viwanda vya zege, machimbo na depo za makontena, msingi mkubwa wa mali halisi. Ilianzishwa na inaongozwa na Ally Edha Awadh: mjasiriamali mwenye uzoefu aliyejenga shirika lenye kiwango cha juu cha uaminifu wa mikopo kwa karibu miongo miwili. Uwajibikaji hai wa kampuni kwa jamii katika masoko yote, ukijenga thamani ya chapa, mahusiano mema na jamii na uhusiano endelevu wa kibiashara.","u":"investors.html"},{"id":"pg:investors:4","t":"Mahusiano ya Wawekezaji","s":"Una Nia ya Kuwekeza au Kushirikiana na Lake Group? Wasiliana na timu yetu ya shirika kwa taarifa zaidi kuhusu wasifu wa kifedha wa Kundi na fursa za ushirikiano. © 2026 Lake Group. Haki zote zimehifadhiwa.","u":"investors.html"},{"id":"pg:leadership:0","t":"Uongozi","s":"Wenye maono na wataalamu wa sekta wanaoendesha ukuaji wa Lake Group kote Afrika Mashariki na Kati. Tunaongozwa na Uzoefu. Tunasukumwa na Maono. Timu yetu ya uongozi inaleta pamoja miongo kadhaa ya utaalamu katika nishati, usafirishaji, fedha na uhandisi. Mkurugenzi Mtendaji Mkuu na Mwenyekiti wa Kundi Mwanzilishi wa Lake Group (2006) · Mjasiriamali aliyetambuliwa na Forbes · Kiongozi Kijana wa Biashara wa Mwaka, African Leadership Magazine 2022","u":"leadership.html"},{"id":"pg:leadership:1","t":"Uongozi","s":"Bwana Awadh alianzisha Lake Oil akiwa na miaka 27 na kuikuza hadi kuwa mojawapo ya makundi makubwa zaidi ya nishati, usafirishaji na viwanda Afrika Mashariki na Kati, likifanya kazi Tanzania, Kenya, Zambia, DRC, Burundi, Rwanda, Ethiopia na Msumbiji likiwa na wafanyakazi 4,600+ kutoka mataifa 21. \"Tukiwa na timu ya wahandisi wenye uzoefu na wataalamu wa biashara katika vitengo vyetu, Lake Group iko tayari kikamilifu kukidhi mahitaji ya soko la dunia, kuanzia uuzaji wa mafuta na usafirishaji hadi LPG, chuma, mafuta ya kulainisha na zege.\"","u":"leadership.html"},{"id":"pg:leadership:2","t":"Uongozi","s":"Chini ya uongozi wake, Kundi limepanuka na kuwa na Lake Trans, Lake Gas, Lake Lubes, Lake Steel, Gulf Concrete & Cement Products, African Inland Container Depot pamoja na mitandao ya kikanda ya kuhifadhi mafuta na rejareja. Mwaka 2023 alitunukiwa pia tuzo ya Kiongozi Kijana wa Nishati Afrika wa Mwaka katika African Business Leadership Awards.","u":"leadership.html"},{"id":"pg:leadership:3","t":"Uongozi","s":"Menejimenti ya Kundi na Lake Oil Watendaji wanaosimamia shughuli za kila siku za Lake Group, watu wake na ukuaji wa kimkakati. Mkurugenzi Mkuu · Lake Oil Tanzania Anaongoza usambazaji wa mafuta ya petroli wa Lake Oil, mtandao wa rejareja na ushirikiano wa kikampuni, akiiwakilisha kampuni kinara katika matukio makubwa ya kisekta na kijamii kote Tanzania.","u":"leadership.html"},{"id":"pg:leadership:4","t":"Uongozi","s":"Mkurugenzi Mtendaji · Lake Group Anasimamia shughuli za utendaji za Kundi zima na kuiwakilisha Lake Group katika miradi ya uwajibikaji kwa jamii, misaada kwa hospitali na programu za kuhudumia jamii kote Dar es Salaam. Mkurugenzi wa Rasilimali Watu · Lake Oil Anaongoza mkakati wa watu na maendeleo ya wafanyakazi kwa Lake Oil, akiisaidia timu ya Kundi yenye wataalamu 4,600+ wa asili mbalimbali kote Afrika Mashariki na Kati.","u":"leadership.html"},{"id":"pg:leadership:5","t":"Uongozi","s":"Anasimamia miradi mikubwa ya Kundi ikiwemo mradi mpya wa Lake Agro na kuratibu juhudi za misaada ya kibinadamu kama vile msaada wa maafa ya mafuriko Rufiji na mikoa ya pwani. Kampuni Zilizo Chini ya Lake Group Kila kampuni tanzu inaongozwa na wataalamu wa sekta katika mafuta na gesi, usafirishaji, uhandisi, utengenezaji na huduma za bandari.","u":"leadership.html"},{"id":"pg:leadership:6","t":"Uongozi","s":"Kampuni kiongozi ya uagizaji wa mafuta, uendeshaji wa maghala na mtandao wa rejareja  miongoni mwa wasambazaji watano wakubwa wa mafuta Tanzania. MD: Abdulrahman Mohamed Msafara wa usafirishaji wa malori 700+ kwa mafuta ya petroli, mizigo mikavu na usafirishaji wa kuvuka mipaka kote Afrika Mashariki. Ujazaji wa LPG, mitungi ya composite na ghala kubwa zaidi la kuhifadhi LPG Afrika Mashariki lililopo Tanga.","u":"leadership.html"},{"id":"pg:leadership:7","t":"Uongozi","s":"Kiwanda cha kuchanganya mafuta ya kulainisha jijini Dar es Salaam kinachozalisha grisi na mafuta ya injini kwa masoko ya kikanda. Utengenezaji wa chuma ikiwemo nondo za HS-CR na vifaa vya ujenzi kwa miradi ya miundombinu. Gulf Concrete & Cement Products (GCCP) Zege tayari na kokoto, kinara wa soko la ugavi wa zege jijini Dar es Salaam. African Inland Container Depot (AFICD)","u":"leadership.html"},{"id":"pg:leadership:8","t":"Uongozi","s":"Huduma za ICD, CFS na depo za makontena matupu zenye usafirishaji unaounganishwa na reli Tanzania. Maendeleo ya miradi ya kilimo na miradi mipya. Meneja wa Miradi: Nassoro Abubakari Wafanyakazi wa Lake Group wanaakisi utajiri wa utofauti wa bara la Afrika, wakiwa na wataalamu 4,600+ kutoka mataifa 21 wanaofanya kazi pamoja kuelekea malengo ya pamoja.","u":"leadership.html"},{"id":"pg:leadership:9","t":"Uongozi","s":"© 2026 Lake Group. Haki zote zimehifadhiwa.","u":"leadership.html"},{"id":"pg:logistics:0","t":"Usafiri na Ubebaji wa Mizigo","s":"Usafirishaji na Ubebaji Mizigo Msafara wa malori 700+ unaotoa usafirishaji wa vimiminika kwa wingi na ubebaji wa mizigo wa kikanda kote Afrika Mashariki na Kati. Uti wa Mgongo wa Mnyororo wa Ugavi wa Afrika Mashariki Lake Trans Ltd. ni mojawapo ya waendeshaji wakubwa zaidi wa usafirishaji Afrika Mashariki, ikiendesha msafara wa malori 700+ kwa usafirishaji wa vimiminika kwa wingi, mizigo ya jumla na usafiri wa kikanda wa kuvuka mipaka.","u":"logistics.html"},{"id":"pg:logistics:1","t":"Usafiri na Ubebaji wa Mizigo","s":"Kuanzia malori ya matanki ya mafuta hadi mizigo mikavu, kitengo chetu cha usafirishaji kinahakikisha uwasilishaji wa wakati, salama na wa gharama nafuu hadi maeneo mbalimbali Tanzania, Kenya na Zambia, na katika kanda nzima kwa ujumla. ✓Usafirishaji wa petroli na vimiminika kwa wingi ✓Mizigo mikavu na mizigo ya makontena ✓Usafiri wa kikanda wa kuvuka mipaka","u":"logistics.html"},{"id":"pg:logistics:2","t":"Usafiri na Ubebaji wa Mizigo","s":"✓Uwezo wa kufuatilia msafara kwa wakati halisi ✓Madereva wenye uzoefu na wasimamizi wa njia Umeundwa Mahsusi kwa Barabara za Afrika Matanki maalumu ya vimiminika kwa wingi kwa usafirishaji salama wa mafuta ya petroli, yanayozingatia kikamilifu kanuni za kikanda za bidhaa hatarishi. Malori ya Flatbed na ya Mizigo Malori imara ya flatbed na ya mizigo kwa ajili ya vifaa vya ujenzi, chuma, makontena na mizigo ya jumla.","u":"logistics.html"},{"id":"pg:logistics:3","t":"Usafiri na Ubebaji wa Mizigo","s":"Magari maalumu ya kusafirisha LPG kwa uwasilishaji salama wa mitungi na gesi kwa wingi kote Afrika Mashariki. © 2026 Lake Group. Haki zote zimehifadhiwa.","u":"logistics.html"},{"id":"pg:lpg:0","t":"Gesi ya LPG","s":"Tunawezesha nyumba, migahawa na viwanda katika nchi 7 za Afrika Mashariki kwa mitungi ya LPG salama na ya kuaminika. Lake Gas Ltd. ni kampuni ya kuaminika ya ujazaji na usambazaji wa gesi ya LPG Afrika Mashariki, ikifanya kazi katika nchi 6. Kuanzia mapishi ya nyumbani hadi jikoni kubwa za kibiashara na matumizi ya viwandani, Lake Gas hutoa gesi ya petroli iliyoyeyushwa iliyo salama na ya kuaminika.","u":"lpg.html"},{"id":"pg:lpg:1","t":"Gesi ya LPG","s":"Aina yetu bunifu ya mitungi ya composite, iliyozinduliwa Dar es Salaam, inaashiria mapinduzi mapya katika teknolojia ya gesi ya kupikia, ikichanganya usalama na urembo. Mtungi wa Composite wa 10 Kg Mpya © 2026 Lake Group. Haki zote zimehifadhiwa.","u":"lpg.html"},{"id":"pg:lubricants:0","t":"Vilainishi","s":"Mafuta ya Kulainisha na Bidhaa Zake Vilainishi bora vya magari, viwanda na matumizi maalum vinavyotengenezwa na kusambazwa Afrika Mashariki na Kati. Yameundwa kwa Ufanisi wa Hali ya Juu Lake Lubes Ltd., iliyoanzishwa mwaka 2014, hutengeneza na kusambaza aina mbalimbali za vilainishi na grisi kwa matumizi ya magari, viwanda na matumizi maalum Afrika Mashariki na Kati.","u":"lubricants.html"},{"id":"pg:lubricants:1","t":"Vilainishi","s":"Mafuta yetu ya kulainisha yameundwa kukidhi viwango vya kimataifa, yakitoa ulinzi na ufanisi wa hali ya juu hata katika mazingira magumu zaidi ya utendaji kazi barani Afrika. Mafuta ya Kulainisha ya Magari Mafuta ya injini, vimiminika vya gia na grisi kwa magari ya abiria na ya kibiashara. Mafuta ya Kulainisha ya Viwandani Mafuta imara ya viwandani kwa mashine, kompresa na vifaa vya uzalishaji.","u":"lubricants.html"},{"id":"pg:lubricants:2","t":"Vilainishi","s":"Mafuta ya gia, mafuta ya giaboksi otomatiki, vipoza-radieta, mafuta ya hidroliki na grisi za lithiamu kwa matumizi maalum. Uchambuzi wa mafuta, ushauri wa kiufundi na msaada wa matengenezo kwa wateja wa misafara ya makampuni. © 2026 Lake Group. Haki zote zimehifadhiwa.","u":"lubricants.html"},{"id":"pg:media_center:0","t":"Habari","s":"Waandishi na Vyombo vya Habari Taarifa kwa vyombo vya habari, kauli rasmi, video za kampuni na nyenzo za habari zinazoweza kupakuliwa za Lake Group. Ally Edha Awadh Atunukiwa Tuzo ya Kiongozi Kijana wa Biashara wa Mwaka Mwanzilishi na Mwenyekiti wa Kundi la Lake, Ally Edha Awadh, alipokea tuzo ya Kiongozi Kijana wa Biashara wa Mwaka 2022 ya jarida la African Leadership katika hafla iliyofanyika katika Ukumbi wa House of Lords, London.","u":"media-center.html"},{"id":"pg:media_center:1","t":"Habari","s":"Lake Gas Yapanua Kituo cha LPG cha Tanga hadi Tani 3,000 Lake Gas imepanua kituo chake cha Tanga  kilichofunguliwa kikiwa ghala kubwa zaidi la kuhifadhi LPG Afrika Mashariki  kutoka tani 1,000 hadi tani 3,000, ikiimarisha usambazaji Tanzania na masoko jirani. Lake Gas Yazindua Mitungi ya Kwanza ya LPG ya Komposi Afrika Lake Gas ilizindua mitungi ya LPG ya komposi  isiyolipuka, isiyoshika kutu, nyepesi na inayopitisha mwanga  katika hafla ya uzinduzi Dar es Salaam tarehe 18 Juni 2014, ya kwanza katika soko la Afrika.","u":"media-center.html"},{"id":"pg:media_center:2","t":"Habari","s":"Kwa maombi ya mahojiano, maswali ya waandishi wa habari au ushirikiano wa kihabari, tafadhali wasiliana na timu yetu ya mawasiliano. Jumatatu – Ijumaa, 9:00 – 18:00 EAT © 2026 Lake Group. Haki zote zimehifadhiwa.","u":"media-center.html"},{"id":"pg:news:0","t":"Habari","s":"Habari kutoka kote katika Kundi la Lake  matangazo, upanuzi, uzinduzi wa bidhaa na shughuli za kijamii. Uzinduzi wa Mitungi ya LPG ya Komposi Upanuzi wa Kituo cha LPG cha Tanga Kwa taarifa kwa vyombo vya habari, mahojiano au ushirikiano wa kihabari: Tumia Barua pepe kwa Timu ya Habari © 2026 Lake Group. Haki zote zimehifadhiwa.","u":"news.html"},{"id":"pg:projects:0","t":"Miradi Mikubwa","s":"Maonyesho ya miradi mashuhuri ya ujenzi, miundombinu na ugavi iliyotekelezwa na Lake Group kote Afrika Mashariki. Tukiwezesha Maendeleo ya Afrika Mashariki Kuanzia miradi ya ujenzi ya mamilioni ya dola hadi mikataba ya usafirishaji wa masafa marefu, Lake Group ina ukubwa, utaalamu na vifaa vya kutekeleza. Kituo cha Kuagiza LPG cha Tanga  Kikubwa Zaidi Afrika Mashariki","u":"projects.html"},{"id":"pg:projects:1","t":"Miradi Mikubwa","s":"Lake Gas ilijenga kituo kikubwa zaidi cha kuhifadhi LPG Afrika Mashariki huko Tanga  kilichoanzishwa kwa tani 1,000 na baadaye kupanuliwa hadi tani 3,000  chenye boya maalum la kufungia meli linaloruhusu meli kushusha gesi moja kwa moja kituoni. Mnyororo wa Ugavi wa Petroli Barani Afrika Lake Oil na Lake Trans kwa pamoja zinaendesha mojawapo ya minyororo mikubwa zaidi ya ugavi wa mafuta Afrika Mashariki, zikisambaza mafuta katika nchi 8 kwa malori 700+ yanayofanya kazi saa 24/7.","u":"projects.html"},{"id":"pg:projects:2","t":"Miradi Mikubwa","s":"Kiwanda cha Nondo cha Lake Steel, cha Kwanza Tanzania Mzalishaji wa kwanza wa nondo za HS-CR Tanzania. Kinu cha kusaga chuma kinachoendeshwa kikamilifu kwa kompyuta huko Visiga, Kibaha, hufanya kazi hadi tani 25 kwa saa  uwezo wa tani 100,000 kwa mwaka  na nondo zake zimeidhinishwa kutumika katika miradi ya serikali. MERM Ready Mix, Upanuzi wa Dubai","u":"projects.html"},{"id":"pg:projects:3","t":"Miradi Mikubwa","s":"Middle East Ready Mix LLC (MERM), shughuli ya zege iliyochanganywa tayari ya Kundi la Lake iliyoko Dubai, imekuwa ikizalisha zege tangu 2005 na huhudumia miradi mikubwa ya ujenzi kote Dubai. Mtandao wa Bohari za Makontena za Ndani ya Nchi za Afrika AFICD inaendesha bohari za kimkakati za makontena ndani ya nchi Tanzania, Zambia na Msumbiji, ikipanua uwezo wa bandari hadi maeneo ya bara na kuwezesha biashara bora ya kuvuka mipaka.","u":"projects.html"},{"id":"pg:projects:4","t":"Miradi Mikubwa","s":"Uzinduzi wa Mitungi ya LPG ya Composite Lake Gas iliongoza kuanzisha mitungi ya LPG ya composite Afrika Mashariki; isiyolipuka, nyepesi na inayoonyesha kiwango cha gesi ndani, ikileta mapinduzi katika usalama wa gesi ya kupikia majumbani. Una mradi mkubwa unaohitaji msaada wa nishati, usafirishaji au ugavi wa vifaa vya ujenzi? © 2026 Lake Group. Haki zote zimehifadhiwa.","u":"projects.html"},{"id":"pg:services:0","t":"Huduma ▾","s":"Kuanzia vituo vya mafuta hadi viwanda vya chuma; sekta nane, dira moja, katika nchi nane. Lake Group inafanya kazi katika mnyororo mzima wa thamani wa nishati na viwanda wa Afrika Mashariki na Kati. Miongoni mwa wasambazaji 5 bora wa petroli Tanzania. Vituo vya rejareja 85+, ugavi wa mafuta kwa wingi na uhifadhi. Ujazaji na usambazaji wa LPG wa Lake Gas. Mitungi ya kilo 6, 10, 15 na 38 kwa matumizi ya nyumbani na ya kibiashara katika nchi 6.","u":"services.html"},{"id":"pg:services:1","t":"Huduma ▾","s":"Usafirishaji na Ubebaji Mizigo Lake Trans inaendesha malori 700+ kwa usafirishaji wa vimiminika kwa wingi na mizigo ya kawaida Afrika Mashariki na Kati. GCCP, msambazaji mkuu wa zege tayari wa Dar es Salaam. Kokoto 30,000 m³ kila mwezi. Lake Lubes hutengeneza na kusambaza vilainishi vya magari, viwanda na matumizi maalum katika nchi 5. Mzalishaji wa kwanza wa nondo za HS-CR Tanzania. Uwezo wa kiwanda wa MT 100,000 kwa mwaka.","u":"services.html"},{"id":"pg:services:2","t":"Huduma ▾","s":"Huduma za bohari ya makontena ndani ya nchi na kituo cha mizigo za AFICD na ACFS katika TZ, ZM na MZ. Shughuli katika nchi 8 pamoja na Dubai. Ramani shirikishi ya vituo vyote vya Lake Group. Uko Tayari Kufanya Kazi Pamoja Nasi? Zungumza na timu yetu kuhusu ugavi wa mafuta, usafirishaji, au huduma zetu zozote Afrika Mashariki. © 2026 Lake Group. Haki zote zimehifadhiwa.","u":"services.html"},{"id":"pg:station_locator:0","t":"Tafuta Kituo","s":"Tafuta kituo cha mafuta cha Lake Oil kilicho karibu nawe na uone huduma zinazopatikana  vituo vya Lake Oil viko wazi saa 24. Tafuta kituo cha Lake Oil kilicho karibu nawe kwa jiji au mkoa. Eneo la Viwanda Vidogo la Mikocheni, Dar es Salaam Wazi saa 24 | Petroli, Dizeli, LPG Wazi saa 24 | Petroli, Dizeli, Vilainishi Katikati ya Mji wa Arusha, Arusha","u":"station-locator.html"},{"id":"pg:station_locator:1","t":"Tafuta Kituo","s":"Jiji la Mwanza, Kanda ya Ziwa Victoria Wazi saa 24 | Petroli, Dizeli, Dizeli ya Malori Katikati ya Jiji la Dodoma, Dodoma © 2026 Lake Group. Haki zote zimehifadhiwa. mf. Dar es Salaam, Arusha, Mwanza...","u":"station-locator.html"},{"id":"pg:steel:0","t":"Lake Steel","s":"Mzalishaji wa kwanza Tanzania wa nondo za chuma za HS-CR. Kiwanda kinachoendeshwa kikamilifu kwa kompyuta chenye uwezo wa MT 100,000 kwa mwaka. Wa Kwanza Tanzania. Umejengwa Kudumu. Lake Steel Ltd. ni kampuni ya kwanza Tanzania kuanzisha nondo za kipekee za chuma zenye Nguvu ya Juu na Zinazostahimili Kutu (HS-CR), mabadiliko makubwa kwa sekta ya ujenzi ya Afrika Mashariki.","u":"steel.html"},{"id":"pg:steel:1","t":"Lake Steel","s":"Kiwanda chetu cha kisasa cha kuviringisha chuma, kinachoendeshwa kikamilifu kwa kompyuta na kiotomatiki, kina uwezo wa uzalishaji wa hadi tani 25 kwa saa, sawa na uwezo wa mwaka wa tani 100,000 za nondo bora za chuma. Nondo zetu za HS-CR hudumisha nguvu katika joto la hadi 600°C, ikilinganishwa na 350°C kwa nondo za kawaida, zikitoa faida muhimu za ustahimilivu wa moto kwa miradi mikubwa ya ujenzi.","u":"steel.html"},{"id":"pg:steel:2","t":"Lake Steel","s":"Maji ya ardhini yenye chumvichumvi Bileti hupimwa katika maabara yetu. Malighafi zilizoidhinishwa pekee ndizo huendelea. Bileti hupashwa joto hadi kiwango cha uviringishaji katika tanuru yetu. Uviringishaji unaoendeshwa kwa kompyuta kwa uwezo wa 25T/hr. Udhibiti wa Ubora na Usafirishaji Upimaji wa ubora kwa viwango vya kitaifa na kimataifa kabla ya kusafirishwa.","u":"steel.html"},{"id":"pg:steel:3","t":"Lake Steel","s":"© 2026 Lake Group. Haki zote zimehifadhiwa.","u":"steel.html"},{"id":"pg:sustainability:0","t":"CSR na Uendelevu","s":"Dhamira ya Lake Group kwa uwajibikaji wa kimazingira, mpito kuelekea nishati safi na kupunguza athari za shughuli zetu. Nishati kwa Afrika. Kwa Uwajibikaji. Kama kampuni kubwa ya nishati na usafirishaji inayofanya kazi katika nchi 8, Lake Group inatambua wajibu wake wa kufanya kazi kwa namna inayopunguza athari za kimazingira na kuchangia maendeleo endelevu kote Afrika.","u":"sustainability.html"},{"id":"pg:sustainability:1","t":"CSR na Uendelevu","s":"Mkakati wetu wa uendelevu unajumuisha utunzaji wa mazingira, upatikanaji wa nishati safi ya kupikia, urejeshaji wa ardhi, usimamizi wa taka na upunguzaji wa hatua kwa hatua wa hewa ukaa katika msafara wetu wa usafirishaji. LPG, biashara kuu ya Lake Gas, ina nafasi muhimu katika ajenda ya nishati safi ya kupikia ya Afrika Mashariki: kupunguza utegemezi wa mkaa na kuni, kuboresha ubora wa hewa ndani ya nyumba na kupunguza ukataji miti.","u":"sustainability.html"},{"id":"pg:sustainability:2","t":"CSR na Uendelevu","s":"Mpito kwa Nishati Safi ya Kupikia Lake Gas husambaza LPG katika nchi 6, ikisaidia kaya kuhama kutoka mkaa kwenda upishi safi zaidi. Kila mtungi unaouzwa hupunguza CO₂, uchafuzi wa hewa ndani ya nyumba na shinikizo la ukataji miti. Shughuli za usafirishaji wa mafuta zinaendeshwa kwa lengo la kutomwaga mafuta kabisa. Matangi hukaguliwa mara kwa mara na kufanyiwa matengenezo katika karakana za Kundi zilizoko Kibaha, Kigamboni na Morogoro.","u":"sustainability.html"},{"id":"pg:sustainability:3","t":"CSR na Uendelevu","s":"Machimbo ya GCCP huko Lugoba hutoa kokoto kwa shughuli za zege za Kundi. Tumejizatiti kuchimba kwa uwajibikaji na kurekebisha hatua kwa hatua maeneo yaliyokwisha chimbwa. Uwekezaji unaoendelea katika malori mapya yanayotumia mafuta kwa ufanisi, kupunguza uzalishaji wa hewa chafu kwa kila kilomita katika msafara wetu wa magari 700+ huku tukiboresha uaminifu wa huduma.","u":"sustainability.html"},{"id":"pg:sustainability:4","t":"CSR na Uendelevu","s":"Nchi zenye upatikanaji wa LPG safi kupitia Lake Gas Ajira za wenyeji zilizotengenezwa katika nchi 8 Uvumilivu kwa matukio ya umwagikaji wa mafuta m³ ya kokoto kila mwezi, ikisaidia ujenzi endelevu © 2026 Lake Group. Haki zote zimehifadhiwa.","u":"sustainability.html"}]}}};
